Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fyes-to-equality-greece-pm-ahead-of-vote-on-same-sex-marriage-adoption%2Famp_articleshow%2F107735738.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fyes-to-equality-greece-pm-ahead-of-vote-on-same-sex-marriage-adoption%2Famp_articleshow%2F107735738.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Only%2032%20percent%20of%20voters%20say%20they're%20confident%20in%20Biden's%20mental%20and%20physical%20strength%2C%20but%20overall%20support%20for%20him%20is%20about%20the%20same%20as%20in%202020%3A%20poll%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joe%20Biden%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c5387c917a1dae0244a44f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20answers%20questions%20while%20departing%20the%20White%20House%20on%20January%2030%2C%202024%2C%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20Biden%20is%20scheduled%20to%20travel%20to%20Florida.%3Cp%3EWin%20McNamee%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJust%201%20in%203%20voters%20are%20confident%20in%20Joe%20Biden's%20physical%20and%20mental%20faculties%2C%20per%20a%20new%20poll.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20Biden's%20support%20overall%20is%20roughly%20the%20same%20as%20it%20was%20in%202020.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20week%20ago%2C%20a%20special%20counsel%20report%20alleged%20issues%20with%20Biden's%20age%20and%20memory.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20poll%20from%20Monmouth%20University%20shows%20that%20just%201%20in%203%20voters%20are%20confident%20in%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20physical%20and%20mental%20faculties%2C%20though%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-biden-memory-issues-special-counsel-report-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%202024%20presidential%20candidate%20is%20around%20the%20same%20as%20from%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.monmouth.edu%2Fpolling-institute%2Freports%2Fmonmouthpoll_us_021524%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoll%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20published%20a%20week%20after%20Special%20Counsel%20Robert%20Hur%20released%20his%20report%20into%20Biden's%20handling%20of%20classified%20documents.%20While%20the%20report%20didn't%20recommend%20criminal%20charges%20against%20the%20president%2C%20it%20did%20note%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-forgot-timing-vice-presidency-beau-death-special-counsel-report-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseveral%20concerning%20instances%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20he%20struggled%20to%20remember%20key%20dates%2C%20including%20when%20his%20son%20Beau%20died%20and%20when%20he%20was%20vice%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConducted%20between%20February%208%20to%2012%20with%20902%20US%20adults%2C%20the%20poll%20found%20that%2032%25%20of%20respondents%20felt%20confident%20in%20the%2081-year-old%20Biden's%20%26quot%3Bmental%20%26amp%3B%20physical%20stamina.%26quot%3B%20Comparatively%2C%2051%25%20of%20respondents%20felt%20confident%20in%20that%20of%2077-year-old%20Republican%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%20GOP's%20leading%20presidential%20candidate.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20disparity%2C%20polling%20showed%2C%20in%20part%20comes%20from%20different-aged%20groups%20of%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20survey%2C%20voters%20over%2070%20had%20roughly%20the%20same%20level%20of%20confidence%20in%20both%20Trump%20and%20Biden.%20That%20changes%20drastically%2C%20however%2C%20among%20voters%20younger%20than%2070%20years%20old%2C%20where%2052%25%20were%20confident%20in%20Trump's%20stamina%20compared%20to%20just%2030%25%20in%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20waning%20public%20confidence%20in%20Biden's%20mental%20and%20physical%20strength%2C%20the%20poll%20found%20that%20support%20for%20the%20Democratic%20candidate%20remains%20about%20the%20same%20as%20in%202020%20when%20he%20first%20faced%20off%20against%20Trump%20for%20president.%20The%20polling%20found%20that%2046%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20either%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bprobably%26quot%3B%20would%20vote%20for%20Trump%20in%202024%2C%20while%20just%2044%25%20said%20the%20same%20of%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpercent-of-voters-confident-in-biden-mental-strength-poll-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708038798000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c53be843bb77284ba513a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpercent-of-voters-confident-in-biden-mental-strength-poll-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Comparatively%2C%2051%25%20of%20respondents%20felt%20satisfied%20in%20that%20of%2077-year-old%20Republican%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mhall%40businessinsider.com%20(Madison%20Hall%2CTaylor%20Berman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpercent-of-voters-confident-in-biden-mental-strength-poll-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump's%20hush-money%20trial%20set%20for%20March%2025%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708038784000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107735746%2Cimgsize-9664.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trumps-hush-money-trial-set-for-march-25%2Farticleshow%2F107735737.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107735737.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimes