cleshow%2F107735625.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Atlantic%20diet%20may%20be%20just%20as%20good%20for%20you%20as%20the%20Mediterranean%20diet%20%E2%80%94%20with%20even%20more%20bread%20and%20pasta%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wooden%20table%20featuring%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%20with%20a%20bread%20board%20including%20soft%20cheese%20and%20grapes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce761f6fcb546d2d505df7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Atlantic%20diet%20features%20unprocessed%20whole%20foods%20like%20fresh%20produce%2C%20with%20wine%20in%20moderation%2C%20like%20the%20Mediterranean%20diet.%20The%20different%20is%20that%20it%20includes%20more%20starchy%20carbs%2C%20bread%2C%20and%20dairy%20products%20like%20cheese.%3Cp%3ENatalia%20Van%20Doninck%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Atlantic%20diet%2C%20based%20on%20eating%20habits%20in%20Spain%20and%20Portugal%2C%20may%20help%20prevent%20chronic%20disease.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20similar%20to%20the%20Mediterranean%20diet%2C%20but%20includes%20more%20starchy%20carbs%2C%20dairy%2C%20and%20some%20meat.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20study%20found%20people%20on%20the%20Atlantic%20diet%20had%20a%20lower%20risk%20of%20metabolic%20syndrome%20and%20less%20belly%20fat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20love%20carbs%20and%20want%20to%20eat%20more%20healthfully%2C%20a%20close%20neighbor%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Favoid-most-common-mistakes-following-mediterranean-diet-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20be%20just%20the%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Atlantic%20diet%2C%20based%20on%20traditional%20eating%20habits%20in%20northern%20Spain%20and%20Portugal%2C%20may%20help%20prevent%20chronic%20illness%20and%20promote%20a%20healthy%20metabolism%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20published%20February%207%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamanetworkopen%2Ffullarticle%2F2814624%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJAMA%20Network%20Open%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20new%20research%20suggests%20that%20this%20carb-heavy%2C%20dairy-friendly%20eating%20plan%20may%20have%20similar%20health%20benefits%20to%20the%20much-praised%20Mediterranean%20diet%20in%20protecting%20metabolic%20health%20and%20preventing%20chronic%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Atlantic%20diet%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Atlantic%20diet%20diet%20focuses%20on%20plenty%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-diet-food-list-cheap-easy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elongevity-boosting%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20produce%2C%20olive%20oil%2C%20beans%2C%20seafood%2C%20and%20even%20some%20wine.%20It's%20similar%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmediterrean-diet-healthiest-best-overall-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ranked%20as%20one%20of%20the%20healthiest%20ways%20to%20eat%2C%20emphasizing%20mostly%20unprocessed%20whole%20foods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Atlantic%20diet%20features%20even%20more%20carbs%2C%20specifically%20whole%20grains%20and%20starchy%20foods%20like%20bread%2C%20pasta%2C%20and%20potatoes.%20It%20recommends%20six%20to%20eight%20servings%20of%20these%20a%20day.%20It%20also%20includes%20cheese%20and%20other%20dairy%2C%20along%20with%20lean%20meats%2C%20and%20red%20meat%20in%20moderation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20are%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20Atlantic%20diet%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Santiago%20de%20Compostela%20in%20Spain%20followed%20231%20families%20(including%20518%20people)%20from%20rural%20Spain%20over%20six%20months%2C%20analyzing%20their%20metabolic%20health%20with%20mea