n%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneanderthal-extinction-earth-magnetic-poles-flip-climate-change-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclimate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20low%20fertility%20rates%2C%20wiped%20out%20Neanderthals.%20But%20Slimak%20thinks%20that%2C%20despite%20being%20intellectually%20inferior%2C%20early%20humans%20are%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20if%20it%20weren't%20for%20us%2C%20Neanderthals%20might%20still%20be%20here%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWho%20were%20the%20Neanderthals%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222003%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20Neanderthal%20skeletons%20on%20display%20at%20The%20Smithsonian%20Museum%20of%20Natural%20History%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cbd72294aa8ee8e84af524%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221585%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20pair%20of%20Neanderthal%20skeletons%20at%20The%20Smithsonian%20Museum%20of%20Natural%20History%20show%20how%20the%20species'%20body%20changed%20over%20thousands%20of%20years.%3Cp%3EBill%20O'Leary%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHumans%20and%20Neanderthals%20share%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuman-ancestors-were-down-1300-faced-extinction-900000-years-ago-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecommon%20ancestor%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20dating%20back%20to%20between%20550%2C000%20and%20750%2C000%20years%20ago.%20Compared%20to%20early%20humans%2C%20Neanderthals%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhm.ac.uk%2Fdiscover%2Fwho-were-the-neanderthals.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewere%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20muscular%20with%20a%20prominent%20brow%20and%20less%20pronounced%20chin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeanderthals%20spread%20into%20northwestern%20Europe%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Central%20Asia%2C%20and