the%20cast%20is%20partial%2C%20and%20missing%20bits%20of%20the%20skull%20are%20filled%20in.%20The%20skull%20is%20displayed%20in%20a%20museum%2C%20a%20person%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20background%20looking%20at%20the%20skulls.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657ae89450edbc52a8641b8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221217%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cast%20of%20a%20Neanderthal%20skull%20is%20displayed%20in%20the%20Chemnitz%20State%20Museum%20of%20Archaeology%3Cp%3EHendrik%20Schmidt%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENowell%20said%20that%20while%20direct%20competition%20or%20conflict%20between%20the%20two%20species%20may%20have%20caused%20humans%20to%20take%20over%20the%20site%20Slimak%20studied%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20may%20not%20be%20the%20case%20everywhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHumans'%20superior%20weapons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20have%20found%20relatively%20few%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneanderthals-hunted-cave-lions-feasted-meat-study-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eweapons%20belonging%20to%20Neanderthals%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Slimak%20wrote.%20However%2C%20Neanderthals%20were%20%E2%80%9Cexcellent%20artisans%2C%E2%80%9D%20making%20tools%20with%20%E2%80%9Ca%20creativity%20that%20is%20beyond%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20creativity%20was%20not%20enough%20to%20outwit%20humans%E2%80%99%20regimented%20weapon%20making%2C%20which%20ultimately%20led%20to%20Neanderthals'%20extinction%2C%20according%20to%20Slimak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmodern%20humans%20who%20colonized%20Europe%20produced%20weapons%20that%20were%20both%20more%20numerous%20and%20more%20effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHumans%E2%80%99%20insistence%20on%20standardization%20led%20to%20uniform%20flints%2C%20and%20Neanderthals%E2%80%99%20originality%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20compete.%3C%