20my%20brow%20lifting%20to%20my%20hairline%20in%20surprise%20or%20joy%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20had%20these%20lines%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20(That%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-repair-sun-damaged-skin-according-to-dermatologist-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eneglecting%20sunscreen%20for%20most%20of%20my%2020s%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20raising%20her%20eyebrows%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce49e26fcb546d2d502a72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20grew%20up%2C%20but%20I%20never%20outgrew%20my%20raised%20eyebrows.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20reveal%20getting%20Botox%20to%20everyone%20right%20away%2C%20giving%20no%20explanation%20to%20why%20my%20eyebrows%20suddenly%20ceased%20to%20lift.%20But%20once%20I%20did%2C%20people%20in%20my%20life%20were%20relieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20wondering%20why%20you%20looked%20so%20mad%2C%E2%80%9D%20my%20mom%20said%20over%20the%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20friend%2C%20hearing%20me%20retell%20the%20proposal%20story%2C%20thought%20I%20was%20secretly%20going%20through%20some%20turmoil%2C%20and%20even%20privately%20asked%20my%20other%20friend%20if%20I%20was%20doing%20ok.%20When%20she%20learned%20I%20got%20Botox%2C%20the%20sudden%20lack%20of%20my%20usual%20facial%20expressions%20made%20sense.%20Both%20friends%20laughed%20when%20I%20showed%20them%20the%20proof%3A%20I%20strained%20to%20create%20even%20the%20slightest%20crinkle%20or%20dent%20in%20my%20forehead%2C%20save%20a%20faint%20twitch%20in%20my%20right%20eyebrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20excited%20when%20my%20Botox%20started%20wearing%20off%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%20a%20month%2C%20the%20Botox%20started%20to%20gently%20lose%20its%20grip