E%26quot%3BI%20never%20learned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Flaundry-symbols%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20do%20laundry%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Flaundry-symbols%3Famp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Euntil%20I%20was%20at%20college%20because%20my%20mom%20would%20step%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20once%20had%20a%20problem%20at%20work%2C%20and%20she%20said%2C%20'Should%20I%20call%20your%20boss%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20her%20idea%20was%20to%20make%20me%20dependent%2C%20but%20I%20grew%20rather%20dependent%20on%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurtis%20said%20she'd%20consciously%20decided%20to%20raise%20her%20daughter%2C%20Maisie%2C%206%2C%20and%20son%2C%20Aidan%2C%204%2C%20not%20to%20follow%20in%20her%20footsteps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20something%20to%20be%20said%20about%20teaching%20children%20accountability%20and%20letting%20them%20figure%20out%20their%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20is%20how%20I'm%20raising%20my%20kids.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20she%20thinks%20about%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20them%20as%20she%20ages%3B%20%26quot%3BOne%20day%2C%20she's%20going%20to%20be%20an%20adult.%20And%20one%20day%2C%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20be%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20millennial%20mom%20was%20always%20strict%20about%20scheduled%20nap%20times%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECurtis%20said%20that%20her%20parenting%20style%20differed%20from%20her%20mom's%20in%20other%20ways%2C%20too.%20She%20said%20childrearing%20could%20be%20more%20demanding%20these%20days%20because%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-parents-set-their-kids-up-for-success-2016-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escience%20and%20learning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20Experts%2C%20she%20said%2C%20had%20found%20that%20certain%