nder%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0has%20reached%20meme%20level%20in%20the%20business%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWill%20Valentine%2C%20Lyft's%20former%20head%20of%20communications%2C%20is%20surprised%20these%20errors%20don't%20happen%20more%20often%20at%20big%20companies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20anyone%20leading%20an%20earnings%20process%20should%20obsess%20over%20it%20for%20days%20and%20follow%20the%20'pens%20down'%20rule.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EForty-eight%20hours%20later%2C%20it%20seems%20Lyft's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flyft-ceo-comments-earnings-typo-cfo-job-safe-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eearnings%20mistake%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20reached%20meme%20level%20in%20business%20circles.%20And%2C%20since%20I%20was%20Lyft's%20head%20of%20communications%20from%20early%202016%20through%20the%20end%20of%202019%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20shock%20several%20people%20have%20reached%20out%20on%20the%20topic%2C%20mostly%20asking%20some%20version%20of%20%26quot%3BWTF.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20immediate%20thought%20was%20probably%20the%20same%20as%20most%20people%20when%20I%20heard%20the%20news%3A%20oof%2C%20that's%20a%20really%2C%20really%20bad%20mistake.%20Next%3A%20my%20heart%20broke%20for%20a%20company%20I%20still%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20biggest%20reaction%3F%20It's%20amazing%20that%20something%20like%20this%20doesn't%20happen%20much%20more%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202008%2C%20I've%20held%20the%20pen%20on%2030%2B%20earnings%20scripts%20for%20the%20likes%20of%20Visa%2C%20Pandora%2C%20Lyft%2C%20and%20several%20clients%20at%20Valentine%20Advisors.%20I%20know%20firsthand%20the%20extreme%20level%20of%20complexity%20and%20precision%20required%20to%20birth%20an%20earnings%20report%20every%20three%20months.%20It%20involves%20countless%20hours%20from%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20organization%2C%20including%20top%20execs%2C%20investor%20relations%2C%20finance%2C%20legal%2C%20communications.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20my%20Visa%20days%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20twin%20toddlers%20would%20decamp%20to%20grandma's%20house%20for%20two%20weeks%20because%20we%20knew%20I'd%20be%20fully%20consumed%20with%20the%20earnings%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20%E2%80%94%20amazingly%20%E2%80%94%20the%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20earnings%20cycles%20for%20thousands%20of%20companies%20go%20off%20without%20a%20hitch.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20the%20earnings%20process%20has%20reached%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techtarget.com%2Fsearchnetworking%2Ffeature%2FThe-Holy-Grail-of-five-nines-reliability%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20nines%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20level%20of%20success%2C%20where%20we've%20grown%20to%20reasonably%20expect%20flawless%20execution%20each%20time%2C%20akin%20to%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20reliability%20and%20availability%20seen%20in%20sectors%20like%20telecommunications%20and%20cloud%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20critique%20of%20Lyft%20at%20all.%20Their%20mistake%20was%20a%20very%20big%20one%2C%20but%20it's%20surprising%20it%20doesn't%20happen%20more%20often%20to%20other%20companies.%20That's%20why%20this%20Lyft%20example%20stands%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20when%20you're%20in%20the%20boiler%20room%20on%20an%20earnings%20cycle%2C%20it%20often%20doesn't%20feel%20so%20smooth.%20Humans%20are%2C%20well%2C%20human%2C%20and%20mistakes%20get%20made.%20It%20occasionally%20feels%20like%20important%20balls%20are%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20being%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20%E2%80%94%20coming%20from%20somebody%20who's%20been%20around%20the%20earnings%20block%20a%20few%20times%20%E2%80%94%20here%20are%20my%20three%20suggestions%20for%20anybody%20playing%20a%20leadership%20role%20in%20any%20earnings%20process%2C%20all%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20helping%20your%20company%20avoid%20becoming%20a%20meme%20on%20this%20topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Obsess%20over%20the%20process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20something%20with%20the%20potential%20to%20swing%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20value%2C%20it's%20astonishing%20how%20rarely%20companies%20examine%20their%20internal%20systems%20driving%20an%20earnings%20report.%20Instead%2C%20that%20process%20often%20unfolds%20organically%20based%20on%20habit%2C%20and%20too%20often%2C%20it's%20little%20more%20than%20a%20basic%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarnings%20should%20be%20reviewed%20like%20any%20critical%20system%2C%20rigorously%20examined%20with%20a%20bird's-eye%20view%20of%20who%20does%20what%2C%20when%2C%20why%2C%20and%20how.%20This%20is%20especially%20necessary%20given%20how%20frequently%20executives%20and%20contributors%20can%20change%20in%20an%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%3A%20I%20always%20encourage%20companies%20to%20take%20a%20comprehensive%20look%20at%20their%20entire%20earnings%20system%20down%20to%20exquisite%20detail%20at%20least%20every%2024%20months%2C%20and%20ideally%20every%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E2.%20Set%20a%20%26quot%3Bpens%20down%26quot%3B%20rule%20for%2048%20hours%20before%20release%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20times%20than%20I%20can%20count%2C%20a%20CEO%20or%20CFO%20has%20introduced%20a%20new%20direction%20for%20the%20script%20the%20evening%20before%20the%20earnings%20release%20is%20scheduled%20to%20go%20out.%20Reasons%20vary%20widely%20but%20can%20include%20boundless%20CEO%20creativity%20or%20last-minute%20input%20from%20a%20board%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20creativity%20and%20perfect%20wording%20are%20valuable%2C%20last-minute%20changes%20can%20be%20killers.%20The%20benefits%20of%20these%20changes%20do%20not%20outweigh%20the%20incremental%20risk%20created%20by%20last-second%20scrambles.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESo%20my%20advice%20to%20public%20company%20CEOs%20and%20CFOs%20is%20to%20establish%20and%20adhere%20to%20a%20strict%20%26quot%3Bpens%20down%26quot%3B%20rule%2048%20hours%20before%20your%20release%20is%20set%20to%20go%20out%2C%20both%20for%20the%20script%20and%20release.%20This%20gives%20all%20other%20key%20components%20of%20your%20earnings%20system%20(IR%2C%20finance%2C%20legal%2C%20comms%2C%20and%20others)%20time%20to%20ensure%20every%20detail%20is%20perfect%2C%20helping%20you%20avoid%20problems%20like%20those%20encountered%20by%20Lyft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Ch4%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20creativity%20and%20perfect%20wording%20are%20valuab%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F02%2F14%2Flyft-ceo-takes-blame-for-extra-zero-in-q4-earnings-release.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ele%2C%20last-minute%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Echanges%20can%20be%20killers.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20benefits%20of%20these%20changes%20do%20not%20outweigh%20the%20incremental%20risk%20created%20by%20last-second%20scrambles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstackcdn.com%2Fimage%2Ffetch%2Fw_1456%2Cc_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cq_auto%3Agood%2Cfl_progressive%3Asteep%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%252Fpublic%252Fimages%252F0fdbb66b-f64e-4d98-8f3b-055fc1307ee3_1180x1240.png%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E3.%20Shrink%20the%20room%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20tip%20is%20mostly%20directed%20at%20newly%20public%20companies%20on%20the%20block%2C%20but%20it's%20crucial%20to%20keep%20the%20number%20of%20people%20involved%20in%20the%20earnings%20process%20as%20lean%20as%20possible.%20Similar%20to%20the%20IPO%20process%2C%20you%20may%20find%20many%20employees%20eager%20to%20get%20involved%20with%20the%20earnings%20process%2C%20attracted%20by%20its%20significance%20as%20a%20new%2C%20important%20priority%20within%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20their%20intentions%20are%20almost%20always%20positive%2C%20it's%20essential%20to%20avoid%20team%20bloat%20in%20the%20earnings%20p