-toc-label%3D%5C%22When%20to%20preheat%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20to%20preheat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221885%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20starting%20a%20batch%20of%20french%20fries%20in%20an%20air%20fryer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60f09e61bb790e0018207dd1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPreheat%20an%20air%20fryer%20whenever%20the%20recipe%20tells%20you%20to.%3Cp%3EPlan%20Shooting%202%20%2F%20Imazins%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20manual%20says%20to%20preheat%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20your%20air%20fryer%20model's%20manual%20advises%20that%20you%20preheat%20before%20cooking%2C%20do%20it.%20Follow%20their%20instructions%20for%20preheating%20for%20the%20best%20results.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20recipe%20says%20to%20preheat%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20you're%20using%20a%20trusted%20recipe%20and%20it%20instructs%20you%20to%20preheat%20your%20air%20fryer%2C%20do%20it.%20You%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20achieve%20the%20recipe's%20desired%20outcome%20if%20you%20follow%20the%20instructions%20exactly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrispy%20foods%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20you're%20hoping%20for%20super%20crispy%20results%2C%20you%20generally%20want%20to%20preheat%20the%20air%20fryer.%20Shah%20points%20to%20examples%20like%20french%20fries%20(fresh%20or%20frozen)%20and%20chicken%20wings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20in%20doubt%2C%20preheat%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20you're%20still%20unsure%20if%20you%20should%20preheat%20your%20air%20fryer%2C%20then%20go%20ahead%20and%20preheat.%20Since%20it's%20simply%20the%20appliance%20using%20one%20of%20its%20normal%20functions%2C%20it%20won't%20damage%20it%20to%20preheat%20and%20your%20finished%20dish%20will%20likely%20be%20crispier.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22When%20not%20to%20preheat%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20not%20to%20preheat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20manual%20says%20not%20to%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20your%20model's%20manual%20specifically%20instructs%20you%20not%20to%20preheat%2C%20then%20don't%20do%20it.%20Some%20manuals%20simply%20don't%20mention%20preheating%2C%20which%20means%20it's%20not%20necessary%20but%20likely%20won't%20cause%20any%20issues%20if%20you%20choose%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20recipe%20says%20not%20to%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20it's%20a%20well-written%20recipe%2C%20the%20author%20will%20have%20tested%20it%20using%20their%20exact%20instructions.%20Preheating%20might%20alter%20the%20cook%20time%20and%20the%20results%20slightly%2C%20so%20it's%20best%20to%20follow%20it%20as%20written.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EReheating%20leftovers%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20you%20can%20certainly%20preheat%20before%20heating%20up%20leftovers%2C%20it's%20typically%20not%20necessary.%20If%20you're%20short%20on%20time%2C%20skip%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20preheat%20an%20air%20fryer%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20preheat%20an%20air%20fryer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20checking%20his%20laptop%20while%20he%20programs%20his%20air%20fryer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61b129d1cb6f11001a79c807%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221302%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPreheat%20the%20air%20fryer%20before%20you%20add%20food.%3Cp%3EzGel%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20switch%20on%20your%20air%20fryer%2C%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20manual%20for%20your%20specific%20model%20and%20find%20the%20preheating%20guidance.%20Preheat%20settings%2C%20automatic%20preheat%20times%20built%20into%20setting%20the%20temperature%20and%20cook%20time%2C%20and%20manual