fused%20to%20dismiss%20a%20hush%20money%20case%20against%20the%20former%20president%20and%20set%20the%20trial%20for%2025%20March.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A87%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68311139%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68311139.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68311139.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Union%20Ministers%20Hold%20Talks%20With%20Farmer%20Union%20Leaders%20Amid%20Protests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThree%20Union%20ministers%20held%20a%20third%20round%20of%20talks%20with%20the%20leaders%20of%20protesting%20farmer%20unions%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Thursday%2C%20amid%20a%20standoff%20between%20the%20protesters%20and%20security%20personnel%20at%20two%20points%20on%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20also%20joined%20the%20meeting%20at%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20State%20Institute%20of%20Public%20Administration%20in%20Sector%2026%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Agriculture%20and%20Farmer%20Welfare%20Minister%20Arjun%20Munda%2C%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20and%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Affairs%20Nityanand%20Rai%20represented%20the%20Centre%20at%20the%20meeting%20over%20the%20farmer%20unions'%20various%20demands%2C%20including%20a%20law%20guaranteeing%20a%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20for%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talks%20were%20underway%20till%20late%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20third%20round%20of%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%20The%20two%20previous%20rounds%20of%20dialogue%20on%20February%208%20and%2012%20remained%20inconclusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20farmer%20leaders%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20meeting%20are%20SKM%20(Non-Political)%20leader%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%20and%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%20general%20secretary%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(Non-Political)%20and%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20have%20given%20a%20%26quot%3BDelhi%20Chalo%26quot%3B%20call%20to%20press%20the%20BJP-led%20Centre%20to%20accept%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20from%20Punjab%20began%20their%20march%20to%20the%20national%20capital%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20but%20were%20stopped%20by%20security%20personnel%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20border%20points%20between%20Delhi%20and%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protesting%20farmers%20have%20been%20camping%20at%20the%20border%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20farmer%20leaders%20had%20said%20they%20would%20not%20make%20any%20fresh%20attempt%20to%20move%20towards%20Delhi%20till%20the%20meeting%20with%20the%20ministers%20was%20held%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20next%20course%20of%20action%20would%20be%20decided%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20Centre's%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20farmers%20squatted%20on%20railway%20tracks%20at%20many%20places%20in%20Punjab%20over%20the%20Haryana%20Police's%20action%20against%20the%20%26quot%3BDelhi%20Chalo%26quot%3B%20protesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Ekta%20Ugrahan)%20and%20the%20BKU%20Dakaunda%20(Dhaner)%20gave%20the%20%26quot%3Brail%20roko%26quot%3B%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20taken%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20use%20of%20tear-gas%20shells%20and%20water%20cannons%20against%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20by%20the%20Haryana%20security%20personnel%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20border%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20the%20call%20of%20the%20SKM%2C%20farmers%20also%20staged%20demonstrations%20at%20several%20toll%20plazas%20in%20Punjab%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20Haryana%20Police's%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20forced%20the%20toll%20authorities%20to%20let%20go%20of%20commuters%20without%20charging%20them%20a%20toll%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20farmers%2C%20mainly%20from%20Punjab%2C%20had%20clashed%20with%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20at%20two%20border%20points%20between%20the%20states%2C%20facing%20tear%20gas%20and%20water%20cannons%20as%20they%20tried%20to%20break%20the%20barricades%20blocking%20their%20march%20to%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20on%20MSP%2C%20the%20farmers%20are%20demanding%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission's%20recommendations%2C%20pension%20for%20farmers%20and%20farm%20labourers%2C%20farm%20debt%20waiver%2C%20withdrawal%20of%20police%20cases%20and%20%26quot%3Bjustice%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20violence%2C%20reinstatement%20of%20the%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%2C%202013%20and%20compensation%20for%20the%20families%20of%20the%20farmers%20who%20died%20during%20a%20previous%20agitation%20in%202020-21.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708020960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2d2fucg8_farmers-protest_625x300_15_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-union-ministers-hold-talks-with-farmer-union-leaders-amid-protests-5065452%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20Union%20ministers%20held%20a%20third%20round%20of%20talks%20with%20the%20leaders%20of%20protesting%20farmer%20unions%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Thursday%2C%20amid%20a%20standoff%20between%20the%20protesters%20and%20security%20personnel%20at%20two%20points%20on%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-union-ministers-hold-talks-with-farmer-union-leade