20Court%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20the%20verdict%20has%20been%20delivered%20by%20a%20Constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20top%20court%2C%20he%20said%20the%20judgment%20runs%20into%20hundreds%20of%20pages%20and%20requires%20a%20comprehensive%20study%20before%20a%20structured%20reply%20is%20given%20by%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20government%20headed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20made%20efforts%20to%20reform%20election%20funding%20and%20the%20introduction%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20was%20a%20part%20of%20such%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Prasad%20said%20the%20voters'%20list%20now%20carries%20photographs%20of%20electorates%20while%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20are%20being%20used%20in%20large%20numbers%2C%20curbing%20the%20menace%20of%20booth-capturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20(bonds)%20was%20also%20a%20part%20of%20similar%20sincere%20efforts%20to%20make%20elections%20transparent.%20The%20honourable%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20given%20its%20judgment%20and%20we%20respect%20it.%20What%20we%20have%20to%20say%20on%20the%20verdict%20will%20be%20decided%20after%20going%20through%20the%20verdict%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Congress%20which%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20bonds%20could%20also%20work%20as%20a%20bribe%20to%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20from%20corporate%20groups%2C%20he%20said%20the%20parties%20whose%20%26quot%3BDNA%20is%20based%20on%20corruption%20and%20bribery%26quot%3B%20should%20not%20level%20such%20charges%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20claims%20that%20electoral%20bonds%20denied%20opposition%20parties%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20in%20elections%2C%20he%20said%20it%20is%20for%20people%20to%20decide%20who%20are%20in%20the%20field%20and%20who%20are%20out%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20have%20thrown%20some%20parties%20out%20of%20the%20field%20and%20they%20could%20not%20not%20win%20even%20one%20seat%20in%20regions%20which%20used%20to%20be%20their%20strongholds%2C%20he%20said%20in%20a%20clear%20swipe%20at%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20spokesperson%20Nalin%20Kohli%20accused%20the%20opposition%20parties%20of%20politicising%20the%20issue%20as%20they%20do%20not%20have%20any%20alternative%20to%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%20and%20the%20positive%20work%20done%20by%20his%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20reaction%20came%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20a%20landmark%20judgment%20annulled%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20due%20in%20April-May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20practise%20in%20courts%20and%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20cases%20are%20won%20and%20lost%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kohli%20told%20PTI%20when%20asked%20for%20his%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20order%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20or%20its%20judgment%20has%20to%20be%20accepted%20and%20respected%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20those%20political%20parties%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20politicise%20it%20are%20doing%20it%20primarily%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20they%20have%20no%20answer%20or%20alternative%20to%20Modi%20ji's%20leadership%20and%20the%20positive%20work%20done%20by%20his%20government%20where%20crores%20of%20people%20have%20benefitted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20said%20India%20has%20now%20become%20the%20fifth%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20from%20the%2010th%20largest%20economy%20and%20it%20is%20on%20its%20way%20to%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20political%20parties%20find%20themselves%20in%20a%20position%20that%20an%20alliance%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20craft%20is%20almost%20dying%20itself%20or%20it's%20dying%20out%20or%20collapsing%20even%20before%20it%20could%20stand%20on%20its%20legs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20their%20reason%20for%20politicising%20it%20is%20very%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kohli%20said%20the%20government%20had%20brought%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20use%20of%20black%20money%20in%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20largest%20perspective%20is%20that%20this%20has%20been%20a%20journey%20for%20several%20decades%20and%20a%20concern%20has%20been%20how%20to%20prevent%20black%20money%20or%20slush%20money%20getting%20into%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKeeping%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20identities%20of%20the%20contributors%20in%20the%20mind%2C%20a%20(electoral%20bond)%20scheme%20came.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20held%20that%20this%20scheme%20in%20this%20format%20could%20not%20have%20been%20there.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20passed%20a%20set%20of%20directions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20has%20%26quot%3Bbasically%26quot%3B%20said%20today%20that%20in%20electoral%20bonds%20the%20information%20should%20come%20out%2C%20Mr%20Kohli%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bany%20order%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20or%20its%20judgment%20has%20to%20be%20accepted%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20said%20the%20government's%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20violates%20the%20constitutional%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20as%20well%20as%20the%20right%20to%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20parties%20welcomed%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20verdict%20and%20attacked%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20the%20court%20has%20struck%20down%20a%20%26quot%3Bblack%20money%20conversion%26quot%3B%20scheme%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20hoped%20it%20would%20stop%20resorting%20to%20%26quot%3Bsuch%20mischievous%20ideas%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20future%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3