ers%20Breivik%20killed%20eight%20people%20with%20a%20car%20bomb%20in%20Oslo%20and%20shot%20dead%2069%20at%20a%20youth%20camp%20in%202011.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68310127%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68310127.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68310127.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHe%20Made%20Himself...%26quot%3B%3A%20SRK's%20Baazigar%20Co-Star%20Johny%20On%20Working%20With%20The%20Actor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor-comedian%20Johny%20Lever%2C%20who%20has%20starred%20alongside%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20in%20several%20films%2C%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20recalled%20working%20with%20the%20star%20through%20the%201990s%20and%20also%20shared%20how%20during%20the%20shoot%20of%20%3Cem%3EBaazigar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20was%20way%20more%20popular%20than%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan.%20Johnny%20Lever%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F%253cblockquote%2520class%3D%2522instagr%5C%22%3EYouTuber%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20working%20together%20in%20%3Cem%3EBaazigar%3C%2Fem%3E%20back%20in%201991.%20He%20had%20done%20Raju%20Ban%20Gaya%20Gentleman%20and%20a%20few%20other%20films%20by%20then%20but%20I%20was%20more%20famous%20than%20him%20at%20that%20time.%20Even%20during%20the%20shoot%2C%20more%20people%20knew%20me.%20I%20was%20a%20star%20back%20then%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20was%20upcoming.%20We%20had%20great%20understanding.%E2%80%9D%20Johnny%20then%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20never%20seen%20anyone%20as%20hardworking%20as%20him%2C%20so%20hardworking.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20actor%20also%20shard%20how%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20was%20not%20good%20at%20performing%20action%20sequences%20and%20dance%20but%20he%20worked%20hard%20and%20made%20sure%20that%20he%20performed%20them%20well%20enough.%20%E2%80%9CShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20was%20not%20good%20at%20fight%20sequences%2C%20he%20was%20not%20good%20at%20dance%20also%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20and%20later%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20made%20himself%20what%20he%20is%20by%20working%20hard.%20He%20became%20good%20at%20fights%20and%20dance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Johny%20Lever%20worked%20in%20films%20like%20%3Cem%3EKuch%20Kuch%20Hota%20Hia%2C%20Dilwale%2C%20Karan%20Arjun%2C%20Baazigar%2C%20Kabhi%20Khushi%20Kabhie%20Gham%2C%20Asoka%2C%20Koyla%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20name%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20disclosed%20that%20he%20was%20offered%20a%20role%20in%20the%20Oscar-winning%20film%2C%20%3Cem%3ESlumdog%20Millionaire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20actor%20revealed%20his%20reasons%20for%20declining%20the%20role%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EKaun%20Banega%20Crorepati%3C%2Fem%3E%20show%20host%20in%20the%20movie.%20During%20the%20World%20Government%20Summit%202024%20in%20Dubai%2C%20SRK%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20Slumdog%20%5BMillionaire%5D%20was%20there%2C%20now%20that%20you%20mention%20it.%20And%20I%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20with%20Mr.%20Boyle%20(Danny%20Boyle).%20He's%20very%20sweet.%20But%20I%20was%20doing%20Kaun%20Banega%20Crorepati%20on%20television%2C%20successfully%20at%20that%20time.%20And%20I%20just%20felt%20in%20the%20story%20that%20was%20being%20told%2C%20the%20guy%20who%20was%20hosting%20was%20very%20mean%2C%20in%20the%20story%20that%20was%20being%20told.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20Rajkumar%20Hirani's%20%3Cem%3EDunki.%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20film%20is%20currently%20streaming%20on%20OTT%20platform%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708018260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fsegi4ivg_kareena-_625x300_15_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshah-rukh-khans-baazigar-co-star-johny-lever-on-working-with-the-actor-he-made-himself-wh