irstyles%2C%20with%20Navya%20revealing%20her%20grandfather's%20disapproval%20of%20the%20women%20in%20the%20family%20opting%20for%20cutting%20their%20hair%20short.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnavya-naveli-nanda-reveals-amitabh-bachchan-disapproves-of-short-haircuts-for-women-in-family-shweta-bachchan-recalls-fighting-with-abhishek-bachchan%2Farticleshow%2F107731641.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCongress%20Changing%20Is%20Not%20The%20Problem%2C%20Not%20Changing%20Is%26quot%3B%3A%20Ashok%20Chavan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExplaining%20his%20shock%20exit%20from%20a%20party%20he%20had%20been%20a%20part%20of%20for%2038%20years%2C%20former%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%20has%20said%20the%20Congress%20is%20%26quot%3Bsinking%26quot%3B%20and%20discontent%20is%20brewing%20among%20its%20ranks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Chavan%2C%20who%20has%20been%20nominated%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20polls%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bmood%20of%20the%20nation%26quot%3B%20is%20in%20favour%20of%20his%20new%20party%20and%20its%20track%20record%20on%20development%20is%20for%20all%20to%20see.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20claims%20that%20he%20quit%20the%20Congress%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20get%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20nomination%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20truth%20to%20this.%20I%20have%20been%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20twice%20and%20an%20MLA%20several%20times.%20I%20could%20have%20asked%20the%20Congress%20to%20nominate%20me.%20The%20state%20of%20the%20Congress%20vis-a-vis%20the%20BJP...%20I%20don't%20see%20them%20ready%20for%20a%20fight%20in%20the%20state.%20If%20you%20don't%20fight%2C%20how%20will%20you%20win%3F%20There%20is%20no%20preparation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTime%20has%20been%20wasted%20for%20the%20last%20year%20and%20a%20half.%20I%20think%20a%20better%20opportunity%20lies...%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20me%20getting%20elected%20alone%3F%20I%20would%20say%20the%20mood%20of%20the%20nation%20is%20increasing%20in%20the%20BJP's%20favour%20by%20the%20day%20and%20the%20opposition%20is%20getting%20weaker.%20The%20work%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20done%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20been%20amazing%20and%20it%20is%20visible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Congress%20saying%20that%20its%20doors%20are%20open%20for%20him%20and%20he%20should%20explain%20why%20he%20chose%20to%20leave%2C%20Mr%20Chavan%20said%20-%20in%20a%20possible%20reference%20to%20the%20Adarsh%20scam%20that%20led%20to%20his%20resignation%20as%20chief%20minister%20in%202010%20-%20%C2%A0that%20he%20faced%20many%20difficulties%20that%20were%20%26quot%3Bpolitically%20created%26quot%3B%20and%20implied%20that%20he%20did%20not%20get%20enough%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERefusing%20to%20comment%20on%20speculation%20that%20Congress%20leader%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%20was%20speaking%20about%20state%20party%20chief%20Nana%20Patole%20when%20he%20said%20that%20Mr%20Chavan%20had%20quit%20because%20of%20one%20leader%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20appeared%20to%20take%20a%20dig%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20said%20even%20earlier%20that%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20criticise%20anybody%20personally.%20I%20have%20left%20the%20party%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20Even%20if%20they%20introspect%20on%20what%20has%20happened%2C%20it%20is%20good%20for%20them.%20Some%20people%20must%20be%20happy%20that%20their%20competition%20has%20been%20reduced%2C%20that%20is%20also%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Everyone%20Is%20Worried'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chavan%20also%20refuted%20rumours%20that%20he%20had%20wanted%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20emphasised%20that%20he%20had%20worked%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20attended%20every%20meeting%20and%20even%20worked%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20-%20the%20party's%20coalition%20with%20the%20Udhhav%20Thackery%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20-%20right%20till%20the%20last%20day.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20grateful%20to%20the%20BJP%20that%20they%20nominated%20me%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20within%2048%20hours%2C%20so%20they%20must%20have%20seen%20some%20qualities%20in%20me.%20I%20have%20not%20spoken%20to%20any%20Congress%20MLA%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20defect.%20Every%20person%20there%20is%20worried%2C%20they%20have%20problems.%20They%20are%20wondering%20what%20their%20future%20will%20look%20like%2C%20whether%20the%20party%20will%20win%20elections.%20These%20issues%20have%20not%20been%20addressed%20and%20that%20is%20why%20discontent%20is%20brewing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmitting%20that%20he%20had%20been%20worried%20for%20a%20long%20time%20about%20how%20things%20were%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%20he%20took%20the%20decision%20now%20because%20it%20was%20as%20good%20a%20time%20as%20any.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'How%20Will%20You%20Win%3F'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chavan%20was%20one%20of%20only%20two%20Congress%20candidates%20to%20win%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20from%20Maharashtra%20in%202014.%20When%20he%20was%20asked%20what%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20Congress%20between%20then%20and%20now%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20needs%20to%20change.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20not%20changed.%20If%20you%20don't%20focus%20on%20today's%20challenges%2C%20today's%20age%2C%20today's%20aspirations%20and%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20youth%2C%20how%20will%20you%20win%3F%20There'