%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A73%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68309398%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68309398.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68309398.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teacher%20Never%20Spoke%20Against%20Gods%2C%20Protest%20Stage%20Managed%3A%20Karnataka%20School%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20headmistress%20of%20St%20Gerosa%20English%20higher%20primary%20school%20in%20the%20city%20on%20Thursday%20said%20the%20recent%20incident%20in%20which%20a%20teacher%20was%20accused%20of%20making%20anti-Hindu%20remarks%20appears%20to%20be%20stage-managed%2C%20and%20revealed%20that%20she%20was%20pressured%20by%20BJP%20MLA%20Vedavyas%20Kamath%20to%20remove%20the%20teacher%20from%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20seems%20intended%20to%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20school%20which%20has%20been%20imparting%20quality%20education%20with%20minimum%20fees%20in%20the%20past%2060%20years%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20statement%2C%20School%20Headmistress%20Sister%20Anitha%20clarified%20that%20Sr%20Prabha%2C%20the%20teacher%20who%20was%20removed%20from%20her%20post%20following%20allegations%20of%20hurting%20Hindu%20sentiments%2C%20was%20only%20explaining%20a%20poem%20by%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20in%20the%20classroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20teacher%20had%20not%20spoken%20anything%20against%20gods%2C%20but%20explained%20to%20the%20students%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%20poem%20'Work%20is%20Worship'%20by%20Tagore%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20quoting%20the%20full%20text%20of%20the%20poem%20in%20her%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teacher%20had%20explained%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%20poem%20which%20says%20that%20temples%2C%20churches%2C%20and%20mosques%20are%20only%20buildings%20and%20god%20dwells%20in%20human%20hearts%2C%20she%20further%20clarified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20headmistress%20said%20four%20persons%20had%20approached%20her%20on%20February%2010%20with%20a%20complaint%20that%20Sr%20Prabha%20had%20made%20some%20derogatory%20statements%20against%20the%20Hindu%20religion%2C%20and%20she%20had%20assured%20them%20that%20an%20inquiry%20would%20be%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20alleged%20by%20the%20anonymous%20woman%20in%20a%20voice%20message%20that%20has%20gone%20viral%20and%20reiterated%20by%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20Sr%20Prabha%20did%20not%20make%20any%20derogatory%20remarks%20against%20Hinduism%20or%20any%20other%20religion%20or%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20while%20explaining%20the%20poem%2C%20Sr%20Anitha%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20school%20management%20had%20approached%20the%20district%20administration%20stating%20that%20the%20viral%20audio%20message%20was%20far%20from%20the%20truth%20and%20had%20sought%20an%20inquiry%20into%20the%20matter.%20They%20also%20sought%20protection%2C%20fearing%20untoward%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20complaint%20was%20also%20lodged%20with%20the%20police%20to%20take%20action%20in%20the%20instance%20of%20the%20woman's%20audio%20being%20propagated%20and%20thus%20being%20made%20viral%2C%20Sr%20Anitha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2012%2C%20officials%20from%20the%20education%20department%2C%20a%20subject%20expert%20from%20the%20block%20education%20office%20and%20a%20coordinator%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Deputy%20Director%20of%20Public%20Instruction%20visited%20the%20school%20and%20the%20incident%20was%20explained%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20local%20MLA%20Vedavyas%20Kamath%20arrived%20at%20the%20school%20with%20a%20group%20of%20Hindu%20activists%20who%20shouted%20slogans%20against%20the%20school.%20The%20management%20recognised%20him%20as%20the%20MLA%20and%20invited%20him%20inside%20the%20school%2C%20but%20he%20refused%20and%20continued%20the%20protest.%20They%20instigated%20students%20to%20shout%20slogans%20against%20their%20own%20school%2C%20Sr%20Anitha%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Kamath%20wanted%20her%20to%20dismiss%20the%20teacher%20or%20else%20face%20an%20intensified%20agitation%2C%20to%20which%20she%20replied%20that%20she%20cannot%20act%20without%20an%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20mob%20led%20by%20the%20MLA%20pressured%20me%20to%20remove%20the%20teacher%20with%20immediate%20effect.%20With%20no%20other%20go%20and%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%2C%20and%20to%20disperse%20the%20mob%20that%20was%20swelling%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20issue%20a%20statement%20removing%20Sr%20Prabha%20from%20the%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20headmistress%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Sr%20Prabha%20has%20a%20total%20teaching%20experience%20of%2016%20years%20including%20five%20years%20in%20Gerosa%20School.%20%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20no%20complaint%20against%20her%20so%20far.%20The%20critical%20point%20of%20the%20episode%20which%20needs%20to%20be%20probed%20is%20whether%20the%20lady%20who%20spoke%20about%20the%20school%20in%20the%20viral%20audio%20is%20actually%20the%20parent%20of%20a%20Gerosa%20student%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20headmistress%20said%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20protest%20was%20stage%20managed%20to%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20school%2C%20which%20has%20been%20imparting%20quality%20education%20with%20minimum%20fees.%20%26quot%3BWe%2C%20being%20secular%20in%20our%20outlook%20always%20respect%20all%20students%20and%20do%20not%20discriminate%20anyone%20based%20on%20caste%2C%20creed%20or%20religion.%20Every%20year%2C%20we%20celebrate%20Deepavali%2C%20Christmas%20and%20Eid%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708015800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fus4rp1e8_classroom-generic_625x300_14_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fteacher-did-not-hurt-any-religious-sentiments-protest-stage-managed-st-gerosa-school-headmistress-5064465%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20headmistress%20of%20St%20Gerosa%20English%20higher%20primary%20school%20in%20the%20city%20on%20Thursday%20said%20the%20recent%20incident%20in%20which%20a%20teacher%20was%20accused%20of%20making%20anti-Hindu%20remarks%20appears%20to%20be%20stage-managed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fteacher-did-not-hurt-any-religious-sentiments-protest-stage-managed-st-gerosa-school-headmistress-5064465%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fteacher-did-not-hurt-any-religious-sentiments-protest-stage-managed-st-gerosa-school-headmistress-5064465%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fteacher-did-not-hurt-any-religious-sentiments-protest-stage-managed-st-gerosa-school-headmistress-5064465%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ready%20To%20Protect%20Ships%20From%20Houthi%20Missiles%3A%20Navy%20Chief%20Exclusive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20Navy%20warships%20deployed%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Yemen%20have%20been%20tracking%20the%20launch%20of%20anti-ship%20ballistic%20missiles%20and%20cruise%20missiles%20and%20stand%20ready%20to%20intercept%20them%20if%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20have%20been%20keeping%20track%20of%20these%20drones%20and%20missiles%20which%20are%20being%20launched.%20Our%20ships%20have%20very%20powerful%20and%20capable%20sensors%20helping%20us%20remain%20prepared%20in%20a%20combat%20zone.%20The%20deployed%20ships%20are%20very%20capable%20and%20potent%2C%20ready%20to%20respond%20if%20threatened%2C%26quot%3B%20Admiral%20R%20Hari%20Kumar%2C%20the%20Navy%20Chief%2C%20has%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20its%20largest-ever%20deployment%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20and%20Arabian%20Sea%2C%20has%20at%20least%2012%20warships%20deployed%20in%20the%20area%2C%20including%20its%20latest%20Visakhapatnam%20class%20destroyers%2C%20which%20can%20detect%20and%20engage%20incoming%20threats%20using%20Israeli-designed%20Barak%208%20medium%20range%20surface%20to%20air%20missiles%20(MRSAM).%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptains%20of%20warships%20deployed%20in%20the%20area%20have%20been%20given%20robust%20rules%20of%20engagement%20and%20will%20launch%20both%20in%20self-defence%20and%2C%20if%20required%2C%20to%20protect%20merchant%20shipping%20in%20the%20area%20that%20may%20have%20been%20targeted.%C2%A0%20Houthi%20rebels%20have%20launched%20dozens%20on%20attacks%20on%20US%20flagged%20vessels%20or%20ships%20with%20any%20association%20with%20Israel.%C2%A0%20''The%20orders%20are%20very%20clear.%20In%20case%20of%20being%20targeted%2C%20they%20will%20act%20in%20self-defense%20and%20protect%20both%20the%20cargo%20and%20the%20ships.%20However%2C%20so%20far%2C%20we've%20not%20had%20any%20such%20incidents.%C2%A0%20We%20have%20seen%20that%20the%20Houthis%20are%20largely%20carrying%20out%20these%20missile%20attacks.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20Navy%20is%20now%20veering%20around%20to%20the%20impression%20that%20MV%20Chem%20Pluto%2C%20a%20Monrovia-registered%20tanker%20bound%20for%20New%20Mangalore%20Port%2C%20was%20attacked%20by%20a%20combination%20of%20two%20drones%20in%20December%20last%20year.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2012%2C200-tonne%20chemical%20tanker%20was%20sailing%20320%20km%20southwest%20of%20Veraval%20when%20it%20was%20struck%20by%20a%20drone%20which%20penetrated%20its%20hull%2C%20causing%20internal%20damage%2C%20a%20fire%20and%20power%20failure.%20The%20Navy%20believes%20that%20the%20drones%20were%20launched%20from%20Houthi-held%20area%20or%20by%20sympathisers%20of%20Houthi%20forces%20in%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Our%20assessment%20is%20they%20came%20in%20pairs%2C%20one%20carrying%20a%20payload%20and%20the%20other%20carrying%20either%20an%20AI%20sensor%20or%20an%20IR%20sensor.%20We%20have%20yet%20to%20determine%20the%20type%20of%20sensor%20as%20when%20a%20drone%20gets%20damaged%2C%20all%20the%20parts%20cannot%20be%20recovered.%20It%20is%20definitely%20a%20kamikaze%20type%20of%20drone%2C%20escorted%20by%20one%20more%2C%20which%20gives%20the%20information.%20This%20is%20our%20understanding%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20Indian%20Navy%2C%20alive%20to%20the%20threat%20of%20both%20aerial%20and%20semi-submersible%20marine%20drones%2C%20has%20already%20started%20the%20process%20of%20equipping%20its%20ships%20with%20automated%2C%20quick-reaction%20gun%20systems%20with%20a%20high-rate%20of%20fire.%C2%A0%20These%20guns%20are%20designed%20to%20intercept%20incoming%20maritime%20drones%20at%20close%20ranges.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20video%20emerged%20of%20Ukrainian%20sea%20drones%20striking%20the%20large%20Russian%20amphibious%20ship%20Caesar%20Kukikov%20which%20subsequently%20sank.%C2%A0%20Another%20warship%2C%20the%20Ivanovets%2C%20was%20struck%20and%20sunk%20by%20sea%20drones%20about%20two%20weeks%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20announced%20the%20signing%20of%20a%20Rs.1%2C752%20crore%20contract%20with%20Advanced%20Weapon%20Equipment%20India%20Ltd.%20(AWEIL)%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20for%20the%20manufacture%20and%20supply%20of%20463%20made-in-India%20Stabilised%20Remote%20Control%20guns%20''to%20accurately%20engage%20small%20targets%20that%20post%20a%20threat%20to%20ships%20in%20an%20asymmetric%20environment%2C%20both%20by%20day%20and%20night.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''These%20are%20all%20weapons%20which%20are%20either%20nearly%20autonomous%20or%20automatic%2C%20which%20can%20detect%20and%20engage%20a%20target.%20They%20have%20a%20very%20high%20rate%20of%20fire%2C%20and%20they%20can%20be%20used%20at%20very%20close%20quarters.%20These%20weapons%20are%20now%20made%20in%20India.%20The%20technology%20was%20earlier%20brought%20to%20the%20country%20and%20they%20are%20now%20being%20manufactured%20in%20India.%20Their%20installation%20is%20already%20in%20progress%20on%20many%20ships%2C''%20Admiral%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Navy%20is%20also%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20movement%20of%20Chinese%20research%20vessels%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20including%20the%20Xian%20Yang%20Hong%2003%2C%20which%20was%20expected%20to%20dock%20in%20Male%20on%20February%208%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Beijing%20is%20trying%20to%20step-up%20its%20presence%20in%20the%20Maldives%20--%20a%20matter%20of%20diplomatic%20concern%20for%20New%20Delhi%20given%20China's%20growing%20influence%20in%20the%20region.%20While%20nothing%20stops%20Beijing%20from%20launching%20probes%20in%20international%20waters%2C%20the%20Navy%20is%20concerned%20that%20charting%20underwater%20regions%20''may%20have%20military%20applications%20as%20well%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20ability%20to%20deploy%20submarines%20or%20operate%20submarines.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20counter%20China's%20growing%20presence%20in%20the%20waters%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20including%20its%20sale%20of%20advanced%20warships%20and%20submarines%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20is%20looking%20closely%20at%20the%20induction%20of%20nuclear-powered%20fast%20attack%20submarines.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20want%20to%20grow%20into%20a%20well-balanced%20force%20with%20aircraft%20carriers.%20On%20submarines%2C%20there%20is%20a%2030-year%20submarine%20building%20plan%20which%20was%20approved%20in%201989.%20Since%20then%2C%20there%20have%20been%20some%20delays.%20But%20Project%2075%20is%20a%20part%20of%20this%20plan%20and%20will%20fit%20into%20this.%20Subsequently%2C%20out%20of%20the%2024%20submarines%2C%20we%20will%20have%20six%20nuclear%20attack%20submarines.%20We%20would%20like%20to%20make%20it%20ourselves.%20We%20have%20been%20learning%20it%20for%20some%20time%2C%20and%20are%20now%20quite%20confident%20of%20manufacturing%20it.%20This%20proposal%20has%20now%20been%20taken%20up%20and%20is%20currently%20under%20process.%20We%20are%20quite%20hopeful%20it%20will%20come%20through.%20These%20have%20long%20gestation%20periods.%20But%20we%20are%20quite%20confident%20of%20our%20capabilities%2C%20technology%2C%20understanding%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20not%20only%20build%20it%20but%20operate%20it%20as%20well%2C''%20the%20Admiral%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Navy%20presently%20operates%20two%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20the%20home-grown%20INS%20Vikrant%20and%20the%20INS%20Vikramaditya%2C%20an%20older-Russia%20designed%20and%20built%20carrier%20which%20will%20eventually%20have%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20a%20more%20modern%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20chief%20says%20that%20he%20remains%20committed%20to%20this%20acquisition%2C%20particularly%20since%20China%20continues%20to%20build%20carriers%20at%20an%20alarming%20rate.%C2%A0%20''While%20there%20is%20a%20school%20of%20thought%20that%20says%20aircraft%20carriers%20are%20history%2C%20if%20you%20see%20how%20many%20aircraft%20carriers%20are%20being%20built%20in%20various%20countries%2C%20China%20has%20got%20plans%20to%20build%20ten.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20Navy%20remains%20focussed%20on%20new-generation%20Rafale-M%20fighters%2C%20to%20be%20deployed%20on%20the%20new%20carrier%20Vikrant%20to%20eventually%20replace%20its%20older%20Russian-built%20MiG-29K%20fighters%20which%20have%20had%20limited%20success.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20acquisition%20of%20Rafale-Ms%2C%20Admiral%20Kumar%20says%2C%20is%20under%20process.%20''We%20are%20hopeful%20that%20by%20the%20middle%20or%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20once%20the%20contract%20is%20signed%2C%2036%20months%20from%20then%20is%20when%20the%20first%20aircraft%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20delivered%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20though%2C%20the%20Navy%20is%20committed%20to%20a%20twin-engine%20variant%20of%20the%20Indian%20Tejas%20fighter%20which%20should%20be%20available%20for%20induction%20in%20the%202040s.%20''We%20are%20aggressively%20taking%20forward%20the%20case%20for%20the%20Twin%20Engine%20Deck%20Based%20fighter%20(TEDBF)%2C%20and%20that%20will%20become%20the%20mainstay%20of%20both%20the%20carriers%20over%20time%2C''%20the%20Admiral%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708015320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fru718eqg_navy-chief-admiral-r-hari-kumar_625x300_15_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fready-to-protect-ships-from-houthi-missiles-navy-chief-exclusive-5064349%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20Navy%20warships%20deployed%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Yemen%20have%20been%20tracking%20the%20launch%20of%20anti-ship%20ballistic%20missiles%20and%20cruise%20missiles%20and%20stand%20ready%20to%20intercept%20them%20if%20required.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fready-to-protect-ships-from-houthi-missiles-navy-chief-exclusive-5064349%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fready-to-protect-ships-from-houthi-missiles-navy-chief-exclusive-5064349%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fready-to-protect-ships-from-houthi-missiles-navy-chief-exclusive-5064349%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20special%20forces%20launch%20raid%20on%20largest%20functioning%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708015020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-nasser-hospital-gaza_6456772.jpg%3F20240