n%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20passed%20an%20initial%20order%20for%20setting%20up%20a%20medical%20board%20to%20examine%20Naresh%20Goyal's%20medical%20reports%20as%20ED%20sought%20time%20to%20respond%20to%20his%20interim%20bail%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20special%20judge%20for%20cases%20under%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20M%20G%20Deshpande%20had%20allowed%20Naresh%20Goyal%20to%20undergo%20medical%20tests%20by%20private%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20plea%20for%20interim%20bail%2C%20Jet%20Airways%20founder%20Naresh%20Goyal%20said%20malignancy%20was%20revealed%20during%20the%20tests%20undertaken%20by%20the%20private%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20his%20medical%20records%2C%20Naresh%20Goyal%20has%20small%20tumours%20in%20his%20intestine%20(common%20location%20for%20small%20tumours)%2C%20called%20'Neuro%20Endocrine%20Tumours'%20(slow%20growing%20cancer).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20has%20hiatus%20hernia%20of%20about%2035%20cm%20to%2040%20cm%20with%20severe%20reflux%20oesophagitis%2C%20which%20is%20a%20medical%20condition%20that%20occurs%20when%20the%20upper%20part%20of%20stomach%20bulges%20through%20the%20diaphragm%20into%20the%20chest%20cavity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20suggested%20that%20the%20stomach%20will%20have%20to%20be%20brought%20down%20and%20prevent%20acid%20reflux%20by%20long%20term%20medication%20or%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20report%20also%20revealed%20a%20short%20segment%20of%20narrowing%20at%20the%20junction%20of%20the%20mid%20and%20lower%20esophagus%2C%20indicative%20of%20Barrett's%20esophagus%2C%20which%20is%20a%20pre-cancerous%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaresh%20Goyal's%20application%20said%20his%20biopsy%20was%20sent%20for%20histopathological%20analysis%20and%20immunohistochemistry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20findings%20it%20is%20imperative%20Naresh%20Goyal%20undergoes%20a%20PET%20scan%20to%20determine%20the%20stage%20of%20malignancy%2C%20based%20on%20which%20doctors%20will%20be%20able%20to%20determine%20the%20line%20of%20treatment%2C%20including%20surgery%2C%20chemotherapy%2C%20the%20plea%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20have%20advised%20aggressive%20and%20immediate%20line%20of%20treatment%20to%20arrest%20any%20fatal%20issues%20that%20could%20arise%20in%20the%20applicant's%20case%2C%20the%20plea%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecial%20public%20prosecutor%20Sunil%20Gonsalves%20submitted%20that%20a%20medical%20board%20of%20J%20J%20Hospital%20be%20constituted%20as%20instructed%20by%20ED%20and%20Naresh%20Goyal's%20medical%20papers%20be%20referred%20to%20it%20for%20opinion%2C%20after%20which%20the%20ED%20will%20submit%20their%20reply%20with%20more%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGonsalves%20said%20they%20(ED)%20are%20not%20experts%20to%20directly%20rely%20upon%20the%20various%20test%20results%20and%20the%20medical%20papers%20annexed%20to%20Naresh%20Goyal's%20application%20and%20give%20opinion%20and%20file%20reply%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaresh%20Goyal's%20lawyer%20said%20he%20has%20no%20objection%20but%20asserted%20the%20medical%20board%20must%20be%20set%20up%20at%20the%20earliest%20so%20that%20time%20consumed%20in%20the%20process%20does%20not%20affect%20the%20accused's%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20both%20sides%2C%20the%20court%20said%20the%20dean%20of%20JJ%20Hospital%20is%20requested%20to%20constitute%20a%20medical%20board%20as%20requested%20by%20ED%20and%20examine%20Naresh%20Goyal%20thoroughly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20medical%20board%20should%20convey%20its%20candid%20opinion%20to%20the%20court%20by%20February%2020%2C%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20shall%20ascertain%20the%20sickness%20and%20submit%20whether%20the%20proposed%20treatment%20based%20on%20medical%20papers%20of%20Naresh%20Goyal%20is%20available%20at%20JJ%20hospital%2C%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2074-year-old%20businessman%20was%20arrested%20in%20September%202023%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20which%20claimed%20he%20had%20laundered%20money%20and%20siphoned%20off%20loans%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%20538.62%20crore%20given%20to%20Jet%20Airways%20by%20Canara%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20laundering%20case%20stems%20from%20an%20FIR%20of%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20against%20Jet%20Airways%2C%20Naresh%20Goyal%2C%20his%20wife%20Anita%20and%20some%20former%20executives%20of%20the%20now-grounded%20carrier%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20bank%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708014360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2F2fkb79j_naresh-goyal-afp_650x400_25_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjet-airways-founder-naresh-goyal-seeks-bail-for-treatment-of-slow-growing-cancer-5064861%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jet%20Airways%20founder%20Naresh%20Goyal%2C%20an%20accused%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%2C%20on%20Thursday%20moved%20a%20plea%20before%20a%20special%20court%20here%20seeking%20interim%20bail%20for%20treatment%20of%20malignancy%2C%20which%20was%20revealed%20during%20tests%20conducted%20by%20private%20doctors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjet-airways-founder-naresh-goyal-seeks-bail-for-treatment-of-slow-growing-cancer-5064861%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjet-airways-founder-naresh-goyal-seeks-bail-for-treatment-of-slow-growing-cancer-5064861%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjet-airways-founder-naresh-goyal-seeks-bail-for-treatment-of-slow-growing-cancer-5064861%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Umbrella%20Academy%20season%204%20relea