%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Needs%20to%20Be%20Disclosed%20by%20March%2031%3A%205%20Charts%20to%20Gauge%20the%20Cash%20Flow%20Through%20Electoral%20Bonds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15213318%2FThe-unemployment-situation-2.gif%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20declared%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20which%20allowed%20individuals%20and%20companies%20in%20India%20to%20donate%20anonymously%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20unconstitutional.%20It%20has%20ordered%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20furnish%20details%20on%20donations%20and%20the%20political%20parties%20which%20received%20them%2C%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20has%20to%20publish%20the%20numbers%20by%20March%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20only%20indication%20of%20how%20much%20political%20parties%20have%20made%20from%20electoral%20bond%20donations%20are%20the%20amounts%20declared%20by%20the%20parties%20themselves%20in%20their%20Annual%20Audit%20Reports%20submitted%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20%E2%80%93%20part%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20which%20pronounced%20the%20quashing%20verdict%20today%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiveLawIndia%2Fstatus%2F1758077322752844056%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ecited%20these%20figures%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20separate%20but%20concurring%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20figures%2C%20compiled%20by%20Commonwealth%20Human%20Rights%20Initiative%20director%20Venkatesh%20Nayak%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20EC%E2%80%99s%20website%20and%20reports%20published%20by%20the%20Association%20of%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20reflect%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20significant%20and%20towering%20gains%20from%20a%20scheme%20now%20deemed%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20right%20to%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFigures%20filed%20b