tion%20of%20his%20legal%20problems%20to%20fire%20up%20his%20supporters%20and%20denounce%20Democratic%20opponent%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20reiterated%20his%20claim%20that%20the%20charges%20were%20%26quot%3Bjust%20a%20way%20of%20hurting%20me%20in%20the%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20can%20you%20run%20for%20election%20if%20you%20are%20sitting%20in%20a%20courthouse%20in%20Manhattan%20all%20day%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20as%20he%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20hearing%20got%20underway%2C%20Judge%20Juan%20Merchan%20rejected%20Trump's%20request%20for%20dismissal%20or%20delay%2C%20ruling%20that%20jury%20selection%20would%20begin%20as%20scheduled%20in%20late%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ex-president's%20legal%20team%20argued%20he%20would%20not%20receive%20a%20fair%20trial%20in%20New%20York%20because%20another%20Manhattan%20jury%20had%20awarded%20%2483%20million%20to%20E.%20Jean%20Carroll%2C%20a%20writer%20whom%20Trump%20was%20found%20to%20have%20sexually%20assaulted%20and%20defamed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20rejected%20that%2C%20as%20well%20as%20arguments%20by%20Trump's%20lawyers%20that%20there%20was%20too%20much%20media%20coverage%20for%20a%20jury%20to%20be%20unbiased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20all%20the%20information%20I%20have%20before%20me%2C%20we%20are%20moving%20ahead%20to%20jury%20selection%20on%20March%2025%2C%26quot%3B%20Merchan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20who%20wore%20a%20trademark%20red%20tie%20and%20dark%20suit%2C%20fidgeted%20in%20his%20seat%20as%20his%20lawyer%20argued%20with%20the%20judge%20and%20prosecutors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20president%20faces%2034%20counts%20of%20accounting%20fraud%20linked%20to%20payments%20to%20porn%20star%20Stormy%20Daniels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20say%20that%20Trump%20illegally%20covered%20up%20remittances%20to%20his%20longtime%20lawyer%20and%20aide%2C%20Michael%20Cohen%2C%20to%20reimburse%20him%20for%20payments%20to%20bury%20stories%20about%20Trump's%20alleged%20extramarital%20sexual%20relations%20with%20Daniels%20and%20a%20Playboy%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegal%20rollercoaster%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20lawyers%20were%20also%20representing%20him%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20Georgia%2C%20where%20he%20is%20accused%20of%20conspiracy%20to%20overturn%20the%202020%20election%2C%20which%20he%20lost%20to%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20hearing%20seeks%20to%20have%20District%20Attorney%20Fani%20Willis%20dismissed%20from%20the%20case%20over%20an%20alleged%20relationship%20with%20another%20prosecutor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20legal%20rollercoaster%20could%20continue%20on%20Friday%20if%2C%20as%20US%20media%20have%20reported%2C%20a%20ruling%20is%20issued%20in%20his%20civil%20fraud%20trial%2C%20in%20which%20he%20is%20accused%20of%20grossly%20inflating%20his%20property's%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20case%2C%20he%20risks%20having%20to%20pay%20up%20to%20%24370%20million%20and%20faces%20a%20ban%20from%20conducting%20business%20in%20New%20York%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%20also%20faces%20another%20possible%20trial%20alleging%20conspiracy%20to%20overturn%20the%202020%20election%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20used%20the%20numerous%20legal%20cases%20to%20fuel%20his%20claims%20of%20being%20victimized%20as%20he%20campaigns%20for%20a%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hush%20money%20case%20dates%20to%20the%20closing%20days%20of%20the%202016%20election%20when%20Trump%20was%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20his%20shock%20win%20as%20a%20political%20outsider%20against%20Democratic%20candidate%20Hillary%20Clinton.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20New%20York%20grand%20jury%20indicted%20Trump%20in%20March%202023%20over%20the%20payments%20made%20to%20Daniels%2C%20whose%20real%20name%20is%20Stephanie%20Clifford.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20say%20the%20money%20was%20paid%20to%20silence%20Daniels%20over%20claims%20she%20had%20a%20t