excessive%20force%20to%20halt%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fas-farmers-head-to-delhi-for-protest-haryana-govt-creates-hurdles-on-their-path%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Chalo%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20began%20on%20February%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scene%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20barrier%20is%20an%20exact%20replay%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%20in%202020%20outside%20Delhi%20borders.%20The%20only%20difference%20is%20that%20the%20farmers%20are%20midway%20through%20their%20journey.%20They%20say%20they%20are%20even%20more%20determined%20to%20confront%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20at%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaspal%20Singh%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Amritsar%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20last%20time%2C%20while%20calling%20off%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20they%20made%20a%20mistake%20by%20believing%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20verbal%20assurances%20on%20enacting%20a%20law%20on%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20as%20well%20as%20other%20demands%20on%20compensation%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20not%20repeat%20this%20mistake%20this%20time.%20We%20will%20not%20return%20home%20until%20the%20Centre%20enacts%20a%20law%20and%20fulfils%20other%20demands%2C%20whether%20it%20takes%20us%2013%20days%2C%2013%20months%20or%2013%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20farmer%20Baltej%20Singh%20from%20Ferozepur%20explained%20why%20a%20guarantee%20on%20the%20MSP%20law%20is%20important%2C%20not%20just%20for%20them%2C%20but%20for%20farmers%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20wheat-paddy%20crop%20cycle%20has%20fully%20destroyed%20Punjab%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20Punjab%20is%20not%20even%20a%20rice%20consumer.%20There%20are%20places%20where%20the%20water%20level%20has%20tanked%20to%20a%20bare%20minimum%20due%20to%20farmers%E2%80%99%20economic%20dependence%20on%20the%20wheat-paddy%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20happening%20because%20of%20the%20faulty%20MSP%20system%20in%20place.%20The%20Centre%20sets%20MSP%20for%2023%20crops%2C%20yet%20there%20is%20no%20provision%20to%20ensure%20that%20crops%20other%20than%20wheat%20and%20paddy%20are%20procured%20at%20the%20government-announced%20MSP.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%2020%20acres%20of%20farmland.%20If%20I%20decide%20to%20shun%20the%20paddy%20crop%20and%20sow%20maize%20or%20pulses%2C%20there%20is%20no%20guarantee%20if%20I%E2%80%99ll%20get%20MSP%20for%20my%20produce%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Punjab%2C%20farmers%20still%20receive%20an%20MSP%20on%20wheat%20and%20paddy%2C%20Baltej%20said.%20However%2C%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20and%20other%20states%2C%20farmers%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20receive%20MSP%20on%20these%20crops%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20saying%20that%20the%20government%20needs%20to%20purchase%20all%20the%20crops%20under%20the%20MSP%20regime.%20However%2C%20it%20can%20at%20least%20bring%20a%20law%20which%20ensures%20that%20the%20MSP%20announced%20on%20crops%20will%20not%20be%20purchased%20below%20government%20rates%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20procured%20by%20the%20government%20or%20private%20agencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15203146%2Fimage-1833.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22957%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15203146%2Fimage-1833.png%20957w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15203146%2Fimage-1833-300x198.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697389%5C%22%20height%