%20By%20Speaker%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20on%20Thursday%20said%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20Speaker%20Rahul%20Narwekar's%20decision%20holding%20the%20faction%20led%20by%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20to%20be%20the%20real%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20was%20%26quot%3Bridiculous%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcopy-paste%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20ruling%20in%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20%26quot%3Binvisible%20power%26quot%3B%20was%20trying%20to%20finish%20off%20the%20NCP%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20both%20important%20Maharashtra-based%20parties%2C%20she%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20can%20you%20expect%20from%20Narwekar%3F%20His%20decision%20is%20laughable%20and%20copy-paste%20of%20what%20he%20has%20done%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20where%20the%20factions%20led%20by%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20had%20filed%20disqualification%20petitions.%20An%20invisible%20power%20is%20actively%20trying%20to%20finish%20off%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20NCP%2C%20two%20important%20state-based%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Baramati%20MP%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20have%20to%20be%20so%20naive%20(to%20expect%20a%20different%20result).%20The%20entire%20country%20is%20being%20run%20by%20bypassing%20rules%2C%20laws%20and%20constitutional%20norms%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sule%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20NCP%20founder%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Mr%20Narwekar's%20observation%20that%20the%20anti-defection%20provisions%20in%20the%20Constitution's%20tenth%20schedule%20should%20not%20be%20used%20to%20suppress%20internal%20dissent%2C%20Ms%20Sule%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20invisible%20power%20dictates%2C%20that%20is%20how%20the%20Speaker's%20office%20functions%20and%20goes%20with%20a%20copy-paste%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20referred%20to%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20Subramanian%20Swamy's%20letter%20to%20BJP%20president%20J%20P%20Nadda%2C%20claiming%20that%20it%20shows%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20party%20conducts%20internal%20elections%20and%20which%20one%20indulges%20in%20suppressing%20dissent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20Tatkare%2C%20Maharashtra%20president%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20expressed%20happiness%20over%20the%20ruling%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20decision%20taken%20under%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20leadership%20last%20year%20(to%20join%20the%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20government)%20was%20upheld%20by%20the%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20happy%20with%20the%20decision.%20The%20Speaker%20has%20studied%20the%20constitution%20and%20given%20his%20verdict%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Ms%20Sule's%20comments%2C%20Mr%20Tatkare%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20have%20become%20frustrated....%20After%20the%202014%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20NCP%20had%20given%20support%20to%20the%20BJP%20from%20outside.%20In%202016-17%2C%20the%20party%20had%20decided%20to%20join%20the%20government%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20discussion%20was%20held%20within%20the%20party%20and%20all%20the%2053%20MLAs%20had%20supported%20it.%20This%20process%20of%20joining%20the%20(BJP)%20government%20was%20going%20on%20for%20a%20long%20time.%26quot%3B%20As%20many%20as%2043%20MLAs%20were%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar%20when%20he%20joined%20the%20state%20government%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20criticised%20the%20Speaker's%20decision%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20on%20expected%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20formed%20the%20NCP%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20it%20now.%20Those%20who%20ran%20away%20with%20the%20party%20are%20the%20new%20heads.%20The%20same%20decision%20was%20made%20in%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20case.%20The%20Speaker%20was%20supposed%20to%20function%20as%20a%20tribunal%2C%20but%20the%20decision%20was%20not%20unexpected%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20state%20minister%20