%20these%20accounts%2C%20a%20potential%20violation%20of%20U.S.%20sanctions%2C''%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techtransparencyproject.org%2Farticles%2Fx-provides-premium-perks-to-hezbollah-other-us-sanctioned-groups%5C%22%3ETTP%20said%20in%20the%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENEW%3A%20X%20is%20providing%20premium%20services%20to%20the%20leaders%20of%20a%20U.S.-designated%20terrorist%20group%20and%20other%20sanctioned%20entities%2C%20according%20to%20new%20research%20from%20TTP.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20arrangement%20may%20be%20a%20violation%20of%20sanctions%20law.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fyt1OI6t70N%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fyt1OI6t70N%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F77gmaAPCgu%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F77gmaAPCgu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Tech%20Transparency%20Project%20(%40TTP_updates)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTTP_updates%2Fstatus%2F1757770327193485573%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E''A%20blue%20checkmark%20account%20that%20bears%20the%20name%20and%20profile%20image%20of%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%2C%20the%20secretary-general%20of%20Hezbollah%2C%20also%20indicates%20it%20is%20''ID%20verified%2C''%20a%20service%20that%20X%20offers%20to%20premium%20subscribers%20as%20a%20way%20to%20prevent%20impersonation%2C''%20the%20report%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22none%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E6)%20The%20account%20for%20Hezbollah%20leader%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20said%20it%20was%20ID%20verified%20by%20X%E2%80%94a%20service%20only%20available%20to%20X%20Premium%20Subscribers.%20This%20requires%20the%20user%20to%20send%20a%20selfie.%