.%20In%20a%20tweet%2C%20it%20wrote%2C%20''Several%20of%20the%20accounts%20listed%20in%20the%20Tech%20Transparency%20Report%20are%20not%20directly%20named%20on%20sanction%20lists%2C%20while%20some%20others%20may%20have%20visible%20account%20check%20marks%20without%20receiving%20any%20services%20that%20would%20be%20subject%20to%20sanctions.%20Our%20teams%20have%20reviewed%20the%20report%20and%20will%20take%20action%20if%20necessary.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EX%20has%20a%20robust%20and%20secure%20approach%20in%20place%20for%20our%20monetization%20features%2C%20adhering%20to%20legal%20obligations%2C%20along%20with%20independent%20screening%20by%20our%20payments%20providers.%20Several%20of%20the%20accounts%20listed%20in%20the%20Tech%20Transparency%20Report%20are%20not%20directly%20named%20on%20sanction%20lists%2C%20while%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjgEzkNcFqj%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjgEzkNcFqj%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Safety%20(%40Safety)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSafety%2Fstatus%2F1757876811793633377%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EX%20has%20now%20removed%20the%20blue%20checkmarks%20from%20the%20organizations%20named%20in%20the%20report%2C%20including%20those%20for%20Hezbollah%20leader%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20and%20Houthi%20rebels%20in%20Yemen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708007880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fq09r8kvo_elon-musk_625x300_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-x-allowed-terrorist-groups-to-buy-blue-ticks-claims-report-5064122%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20report%20claims%20that%20over%20a%20dozen%20X%20accounts%20for%20US-sanctioned%20entities%20had%20a%20blue%20checkmark%2C%20which%2