rd.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnbcc-bags-housing-redevelopment-project-for-mea-worth-rs-262-crore-124021501223_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnbcc-bags-housing-redevelopment-project-for-mea-worth-rs-262-crore-124021501223_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Want%20to%20Donate%20Clothes%2C%20Toys%2C%20Books%3F%20This%20Startup%20Collects%20From%20Your%20Doorsteps%20%26amp%3B%20Delivers%20to%20NGOs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20Akriti%20(%3Cem%3Ename%20changed%3C%2Fem%3E)%20from%20Mumbai%20had%20a%20prized%20possession.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337611%2Fdr-shweta-gupta-ecofriendly-toys-by-little-llama-startup-in-chandigarh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrizzly%20bear%20soft%20toy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20two%20were%20inseparable.%20But%20as%20newer%20friends%20and%20a%20fancy%20mobile%20took%20Grizzly%E2%80%99s%20place%2C%20Akriti%20and%20the%20bear%20grew%20apart.%20In%20the%20years%20to%20come%2C%20it%20was%20confined%20to%20the%20corner%20of%20the%20cupboard%20gathering%20dust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrizzly%20deserved%20a%20new%20life%20and%20an%20enthusiastic%20companion%20once%20more%2C%20thought%20Akriti%20as%20she%20narrowed%20down%20on%20NGOs%20where%20she%20could%20donate%20it.%20Months%20later%2C%20another%20little%20girl%E2%80%99s%20day%20was%20made%20as%20the%20teddy%20bear%20entered%20her%20life.%20The%20circle%20of%20love%20was%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20an%20%3Cem%3Eajji%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmother)%20in%20Bengaluru%20shares%20how%20she%20was%20the%20sole%20caretaker%20of%20her%20two%20grandkids.%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20wash%20their%20clothes%20and%20uniforms%20by%20hand%20every%20day.%20Now%20the%20washing%20machine%20I%20received%20through%20%E2%80%98Share%20At%20Door%20Step%E2%80%99%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2