l%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbdullah%20also%20hinted%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20simultaneous%20assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Political%20parties%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20have%20been%20demanding%20an%20assembly%20election%20ever%20since%20Article%20370%20was%20read%20down.%20The%20Union%20government%20has%20been%20reluctant%20in%20conducting%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20seat%20sharing%20is%20concerned%2C%20I%20want%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20the%20National%20Conference%20will%20contest%20elections%20on%20its%20own%20strength.%20There%20are%20no%20two%20opinions%20about%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20should%20be%20no%20questions%20on%20this%20anymore%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20Abdullah%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%20elections%20in%20both%20states%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20will%20be%20held%20with%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbdullah%E2%80%99s%20decision%20has%20come%20after%20a%20number%20of%20his%20party%20leaders%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region%20joined%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20last%20month.%20The%20delay%20in%20seat-sharing%20talks%20may%20have%20triggered%20the%20announcement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2012%2C%20Abdullah%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fed-summons-farooq-abdullah-for-questioning-in-money-laundering-case-101707748254275.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esummoned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20questioning%20in%20a%20case%20related%20to%20alleged%20financial%20irregularities%20in%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Cricket%20Association.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20veteran%20Kashmir%20leader%20did%20not%20rule%20out%20returning%20to%20the%20NDA%20fold%20in%20the%20future.%20Abdullah%20had%20expressed%20his%20anguish%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%2C%20and%20had%20hinted%20at%20forming%20a%20separate%20alliance%20in%20Kashmir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20chief%20spokesperson%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20responded%20to%20Abdullah%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETalks%20are%20going%20on.%20Every%20party%20has%20their%20own%20limitations.%20National%20Conference%20and%20PDP%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20remain%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbdullah%E2%80%99s%20flip-flop%20may%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20as%20he%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%20advocates%20of%20forming%20a%20united%20opposition%20alliance.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%20opponents%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20recent%20times.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20Abdullah%20asserted%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cto%20safeguard%20the%20nation%2C%20we%20must%20set%20aside%20our%20disagreements%20and%20prioritise%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20welfare.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20unlike%20his%20father%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fomar-abdullah-national-conference-india-bloc-farooq-abdullah-2024-lok-sabha-elections-2502699-2024-02-15%5C%22%3Easserted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20National%20Conference%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarooq%20Abdullah%E2%80%99s%20son%20and%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20said%20that%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20statement%20was%20a%20reflection%20of%20what%20the%20party%20cadre%20feels%20but%20indicated%20that%20the%20NC%E2%80%99s%20talks%20with%20Congress%20and%20PDP%20may%20have%20hit%20a%20roadblock%20over%20its%20interest%20in%20contesting%20a%20few%20seats%20where%20other%20INDIA%20constituents%20in%20the%20valley%20too%20want%20to%20field%20their%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20seat%20sharing%2C%20we%20have%20been%20very%20clear%20for%20the%20last%20few%20months.%20The%20seats%20that%20will%20be%20discussed%20are%20those%20that%20are%20held%20with%20BJP%2C%20we%20are%20firm%20on%20that%20position%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNational%20Conference%20has%20made%20no%20secrets%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20would%20rather%20fight%20elections%20on%20all%20seats%2C%20but%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20sometimes%20for%20a%20bigger%20objective%2C%20small%20sacrifices%20have%20to%20be%20made.%20If%20the%20bigger%20objective%20is%20to%20win%20seats%20back%20from%20the%20BJP%E2%80%A6then%20if%20it%20is%20necessary%20for%20NC%20to%20enter%20into%20seat%20sharing%20with%20Congress%2C%20our%20doors%20are%20open%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20yet%20had%20any%20formal%20discussion%20with%20Congress%20(on%20seat%20sharing)%2C%20informally%20some%20dialogues%20have%20taken%20place.%20We%20are%20not%20the%20sort%20of%20a%20party%20that%20has%20our%20feet%20in%20multiple%20boats%2C%20once%20we%20make%20friends%2C%20we%20stick%20to%20those%20friends%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20recently%20left%20the%20alliance%20and%20joined%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance.%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20also%20exited%20INDIA%20after%20she%20declared%20that%20she%20will%20contest%20alone%20in%20West%20Bengal%20after%20her%20party%E2%80%99s%20talk