fficials%2C%20said%20as%20part%20of%20the%20preparation%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20%E2%80%9Chas%20already%20stocked%20up%20a%20large%20number%20of%20tear%20gas%20shells%20and%20ordered%2030%2C000%20more%20from%20BSF%E2%80%99s%20Tear%20Smoke%20Unite%20located%20at%20Tekanpur%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Gwalior.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20the%20resolve%20of%20the%20police%20force%20under%20the%20ministry%20of%20home%20affairs%20(MHA)%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20let%20the%20protesters%20enter%20the%20national%20capital%E2%80%9D%20the%20news%20report%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20freshly%20ordered%20shells%20are%20being%20brought%20to%20Delhi%20from%20Gwalior.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHundreds%20of%20protesting%20farmers%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20agree%20to%20their%20set%20of%20demands%20including%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20on%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20of%20crops%20and%20loan%20waivers%2C%20have%20assembled%20near%20Ambala%2C%20located%20close%20to%20the%20Shambhu%20border%20between%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20barricading%20the%20state%20border%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20proceed%20through%20the%20state%20to%20reach%20their%20destination%2C%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20has%20been%20using%20tear%20gas%20shells%20on%20them.%20News%20reports%20said%20some%20of%20the%20shells%20were%20dropped%20on%20the%20protesters%20via%20drones%20too.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20farmers%2C%20and%20journalists%20covering%20the%20protests%2C%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Findia-news%2Ftear-gas-shelling-to-flying-kites-to-hinder-drones-recap-of-day-2-of-farmers-delhi-chalo-protest%2F3395028%2F%5C%22%3Ehospitalised%20due%20to%20injuries%20from%20the%20baton%20charge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20reports.%20Farmers%20have%20told%20reporters%20that%20Haryana%20Police%20have%20used%20pellet%20guns%20on%20them%20too%2C%20causing%20injuries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20PTI%20report%20said%20that%20Delhi%20Police%20%E2%80%9Chas%20made%20all%20logistical%20arrangements%20to%20stop%20the%20farmers%20at%20the%20Singhu%20(Sonipat%20side)%2C%20Tikri%20(Bahadurgarh%20side)%20and%20Ghazipur%20(Ghaziabad%20side)%20borders%E2%80%9D.%20Already%2C%20prohibitory%20orders%20under%20section%20144%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC)%20have%20been%20clamped%20across%20the%20national%20capital%20for%20a%20month%2C%20banning%20assembly%20of%20five%20or%20more%20people%3B%20rallies%20and%20demonstrations%2C%20and%20entry%20into%20the%20national%20capital%20of%20tractor-trolleys%20carrying%20people.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707990610000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15143116%2FScreenshot-2024-02-15-at-2.30.52-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-police-orders-30000-tear-gas-shells-ahead-of-farmers-protest-march-towards-the-capital%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20reports%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20%E2%80%9Chas%20made%20all%20logistical%20arrangements%20to%20stop%20the%20farmers%20at%20the%20Singhu%20(Sonipat%20side)%2C%20Tikri%20(Bahadurgarh%20side)%20and%20Ghazipur%20(Ghaziabad%20side)%20borders%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-police-orders-30000-tear-gas-shells-ahead-of-farmers-protest-march-towards-the-capital%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cameron%20loath%20to%20'lecture'%20US%20over%20Ukraine%20-%20after%20Republican's%20'kiss%20my%20a**'%20remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707989520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-david-cameron-najib-