%3Cp%3EInternal%20discontent%20started%20to%20surface%20after%20two%20upper-caste%20leaders%20with%20little%20mass%20base%20or%20role%20in%20active%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20actor%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20and%20retired%20bureaucrat%20Alok%20Ranjan%20%E2%80%93%20were%20among%20the%20three%20candidates%20nominated%20by%20the%20SP%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election.%20Meanwhile%2C%20senior%20OBC%20leader%20Swami%20Prasad%20Maurya%2C%20who%20has%20been%20vocal%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20politics%20and%20Brahmanical%20orthodoxy%2C%20resigned%20from%20the%20post%20of%20national%20general%20secretary%20arguing%20that%20his%20political%20views%20on%20the%20Hindu%20faith%20with%20a%20view%20to%20mobilise%20Dalits%20and%20OBCs%20were%20being%20disregarded%20and%20dismissed%20as%20mere%20personal%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaurya%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20from%20the%20post%20came%20after%20several%20SP%20leaders%20openly%20criticised%20him%20for%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Framcharitramanas-uses-objectionable-language-against-dalits-adivasis-obcs-swami-prasad-maurya%5C%22%3Ecritical%20remarks%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamcharitmanas%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Hindu%20religion%20and%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%20Many%20top%20SP%20leaders%2C%20unhappy%20with%20his%20views%20%E2%80%98against%E2%80%99%20Hindu%20faith%2C%20had%20tried%20to%20cut%20the%20damage%20by%20dismissing%20Maurya%E2%80%99s%20provocative%20statements%20as%20personal%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaurya%2C%20an%20MLC%20known%20for%20his%20firebrand%20Ambedkarite%20Bahujan%20politics%2C%20wrote%20to%20Yadav%20expressing%20his%20grief%20over%20what%20he%20alleged%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdiscrimination%E2%80%9D%20faced%20by%20him%20despite%20enjoying%20a%20high%20ranking%20post%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%2C%20he%20said%20he%20could%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20understand%20how%2C%20as%20a%20national%20general%20secretary%2C%20any%20statement%20of%20mine%20is%20dubbed%20as%20personal%2C%20while%20there%20are%20other%20national%20general%20secretary%20leaders%20whose%20every%20statement%20is%20viewed%20as%20the%20statement%20of%20the%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20perplexing%2C%20he%20argued%2C%20that%20among%20office-bearers%20enjoying%20the%20same%20status%2C%20some%20statements%20were%20considered%20personal%20while%20others%20were%20given%20the%20importance%20of%20official%20party%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20discrimination%20even%20in%20the%20post%20of%20national%20general%20secretary%2C%20then%20I%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20no%20justification%20for%20me%20to%20continue%20in%20such%20a%20discriminatory%20and%20insignificant%20position%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Maurya%2C%20a%20former%20cabinet%20minister%20and%20leader%20of%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20discontent%20ally%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20Maurya%20sent%20the%20letter%2C%20another%20OBC%20leader%2C%20Pallavi%20Patel%20of%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20(Kameravadi)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20only%20remaining%20ally%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20came%20out%20and%20disapproved%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20field%20two%20upper-caste%20leaders%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20while%20ignoring%20the%20PDA%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20is%20technically%20an%20SP%20MLA%20as%20she%20fought%20on%20an%20SP%20symbol%20in%202022%2C%20but%20is%20the%20second-in-command%20of%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20(K)%2C%20which%20has%20pockets%20of%20influence%20among%20the%20Kurmis%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20backward%20castes%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20a%20television%20channel%2C%20hinted%20that%20she%20would%20not%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20candidates%20because%20the%20party%20had%20ignored%20Dalits%2C%20OBCs%20and%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20significant%20as%20the%20SP%2C%20with%20the%20potential%20exit%20of%20the%20nine%20RLD%20MLAs%2C%20is%20already%20one%20short%20of%20ensuring%20that%20its%20third%20candidate%20is%20elected%20unopposed%20without%20any%20contest.%20Any%20rebellion%20by%20OBC%20leaders%20might%20pose%20a%20fresh%20challenge%20for%20the%20SP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20sufficient%20numbers%20to%20get%20seven%20RS%20candidates%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20eight%20BJP%20candidate%20Sanjay%20Seth%20filed%20his%20nomination%20for%20the%20RS%20polls%20on%20Thursday%2C%20meaning%20that%20there%20will%20be%20voting.%20This%20opens%20doors%20for%20cross%20voting%20and%20further%20complicates%20the%20situation%20for%20the%20SP%20and%20its%20candidates%20as%20the%20party%20is%20already%20short%20by%20one%20MLA%20after%20the%20exit%20of%20the%20RLD.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20nine%20RLD%20MLAs%20met%20party%20chief%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20in%20a%20show%20of%20unity%20ahead%20of%20the%20RS%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20said%20that%20she%20would%20not%20want%20to%20be%20party%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Edhokebazi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(fraud)%20where%20the%20%E2%80%9Crights%20of%20the%20PDA%20are%20being%20gobbled%20up%E2%80%9D.%20With%20a%20direct%20dig%20at%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20and%20Alok%20Ranjan%2C%20Patel%20said%20that%20while%20the%20PDA%20slogan%20of%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20meant%20Pichda%20Dalit%20Alpsankhyak%2C%20the%20party%20leadership%20was%20reducing%20it%20to%20a%20party%20of%20%E2%80%9CBachchan%20and%20Ranjan%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20a%20reference%20to%20their%20upper-caste%20surnames.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20actor%20Bachchan%20is%20a%20multiple-time%20MP%2C%20she%20has%20little%20impact%20in%20UP%20politics%20or%20area%20of%20influence.%20Ranjan%2C%20who%20was%20chief%20secretary%20during%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20rule%2C%20after%20retirement%20became%20the%20SP%20leader%E2%80%99s%20advisor.%20He%20too%2C%20though%20adding%20backroom%20value%20through%20his%20administrative%20experience%20and%20expertise%2C%20does%20not%20bring%20any%20new%20votes%20to%20the%20SP%20when%20it%20desperately%20needs%20to%20create%20a%20second-rung%20caste%20leadership%20to%20tackle%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20dismissed%20Ranjan%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Csarkari%20clerk%E2%80%9D%20and%20suggested%20that%20Bachchan%2C%20though%20a%20famous%20actor%2C%20was%20unfit%20to%20represent%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20OBCs%20and%20Dalits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20some%20%3Cem%3Efilmy%20ladai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(movie%20fight).%20This%20is%20a%20fight%20for%20the%20villages%2C%20poor%2C%20Dalit%2C%20backwards%20and%20minorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Patel%2C%20who%20had%20in%202022%20defeated%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20in%20a%20much-hyped%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20want%20their%20votes%20but%20are%20not%20honest%20with%20their%20representation%2C%20I%20will%20not%20be%20involved%20in%20that%20dhokha%20(fraud)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20SP%20improved%20its%20tally%20in%20UP%20from%2047%20to%20111%20as%20it%20built%20alliances%20with%20smaller%20OBC-based%20parties%20and%20also%20accommodated%20senior%20Bahujan%20leaders%20into%20its%20party%20organisation.%20Questions%20are%20also%20being%20raised%20on%20why%20the%20SP%20did%20not%20field%20a%20single%20Muslim%20even%20though%20the%20community%20had%20cast%20its%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20SP%20in%20unprecedented%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20speculation%20that%20Patel%20wanted%20the%20SP%20to%20nominate%20her%20mother%20Krishna%20Patel%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20Kameravadi%2C%20to%20the%20RS.%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20sister%20Anupriya%20Patel%20is%20a%20key%20BJP%20ally%20and%20heads%20the%20other%20faction%20of%20the%20Apna%20Dal%2C%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20(Soneyal).%20The%20two%20parties%20were%20created%20after%20the%20BJP%20engineered%20a%20split%20in%20the%20main%20Apna%20Dal%20party%20to%20appropriate%20the%20legacy%20of%20Sonelal%20Patel%2C%20a%20Kurmi%20leader%20who%20was%20popular%20with%20his%20community%20in%20the%20Allahabad-Varanasi%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaurya%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20from%20the%20national%20general%20secretary%20post%20was%20curiously%20timed%20with%20the%20nominations%20for%20the%20RS%20polls.%20Interestingly%2C%20Patel%20also%20defended%20Maurya%20and%20criticised%20the%20SP%20for%20allowing%20its%20leaders%20to%20target%20him%20for%20his%20comments%20despite%20his%20stature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20not%20sending%20a%20strong%20message%20through%20the%20RS%20polls%2C%20the%20SP%20seems%20to%20have%20missed%20an%20opportunity%20to%20demonstrate%20an%20honesty%20towards%20the%20PDA%20slogan.%20In%20caste%20politics%2C%20representation%20to%20marginalised%20groups%20is%20among%20the%20key%20ways%20of%20connecting%20with%20the%20electorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20in%20previous%20years%20mastered%20this%20art%20by%20appeasing%20lower%20OBCs%20while%20retaining%20the%20trust%20of%20its%20upper-caste%20core%20to%20build%20a%20rainbow%20of%20Hindu%20consolidation.%20Out%20of%20the%20seven%20RS%20candidates%20nominated%20by%20the%20saffron%20party%2C%20four%20are%20OBC.%20These%20are%20former%20Congress%20leader%20R.P.N.%20Singh%20(a%20Sainthwar)%2C%20Amarpal%20Maurya%20(Maurya)%2C%20former%20MP%20Chaudhari%20Tejveer%20Singh%20(Jat)%20and%20former%20MLA%20Sangeeta%20Balwant%20(Bind).%20The%20remaining%20three%20nominees%20are%20upper%20caste%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Brahmin%2C%20a%20Thakur%20and%20a%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20SP%2C%20which%20is%20on%20the%20backfoot%2C%20nominated%20two%20upper%20caste%20leaders%20with%20little%20involvement%20in%20politics%20and%20a%20Dalit%20(former%20MP%20Ramji%20Lal%20Suman).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESP%20leaders%20pile%20criticism%20on%20Maurya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2014%2C%20convening%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Swami%20Prasad%20Maurya%2C%20when%20asked%20if%20he%20would%20now%20also%20resign%20from%20the%20party%2C%20said%20he%20would%20take%20a%20decision%20after%20observing%20Akhilesh%E2%80%99s%20next%20step.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ball%20is%20in%20his%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Maurya%2C%20who%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20political%20career%20in%20the%20Bashujan%20Samaj%20Party%20before%20a%20stint%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20joined%20the%20SP%20ahead%20of%20the%202022%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20start%2C%20he%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20misfit%20in%20the%20SP%2C%20especially%20after%20he%20developed%20a%20knack%20for%20criticising%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20and%20Brahmanical%20supremacy%20for%20subjugating%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%20and%20tribals.%20The%20SP%20has%20for%20long%20believed%20that%20it%20cannot%20replicate%20the%20Dravidian%20model%20of%20politics%20and%20antagonise%20the%20powerful%20and%20numerically%20important%20upper-caste%20voters%20in%20UP%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20threat%20of%20communal%20polarisation%20looming%20large%20and%20a%20divided%20OBC%20and%20Dalit%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20year%2C%20Maurya%20has%20triggered%20political%20controversies%20with%20his%20statements%20which%20range%20from%20demanding%20that%20casteist%20and%20misogynist%20verses%20be%20deleted%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamcharitmanas%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20dismissing%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdhokha%E2%80%9D%20to%20entrap%20gullible%20tribals%2C%20OBCs%20and%20Dalits.%20While%20his%20comments%20have%20attracted%20a%20shoe%20attack%2C%20black%20flags%20and%20an%20ink%20attack%20on%20him%20along%20with%20numerous%20police%20complaints%20and%20calls%20for%20violence%20against%20him%2C%20his%20party%20colleagues%2C%20especially%20UC%2C%20have%20also%20censured%20him%20for%20raking%20up%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20criticism%20against%20Maurya%20is%20two-fold.%20First%2C%20his%20comments%20antagonise%20Hindu%20voters%20in%20a%20deeply%20religious%20and%20conservative%20society.%20Second%2C%20it%20distracts%20the%20narrative%20from%20caste%20mobilisation%20to%20religion%20and%20thus%20poses%20a%20challenge%20of%20communal%20polarisation%20as%20the%20SP%20carries%20the%20baggage%20of%20allegations%20of%20%E2%80%98Muslim%20appeasement%E2%80%99%20and%20catering%20only%20to%20the%20Yadav%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESP%20MP%20Dimple%20Yadav%20in%20December%202023%20distanced%20herself%20from%20Maurya%E2%80%99s%20repeated%20attacks%20on%20the%20Hindu%20faith%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20his%20personal%20views%20and%20did%20not%20reflect%20the%20stand%20of%20the%20SP.%20Months%20before%20that%2C%20senior%20SP%20leader%20Ram%20Gopal%20Yadav%2C%20the%20party%20president%E2%80%99s%20uncle%2C%20had%20also%20tried%20to%20downplay%20Maurya%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20by%20saying%20that%20a%20political%20party%20was%20under%20the%20compulsion%20to%20accommodate%20both%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20and%20crooked%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20SP%20MLA%20Rakesh%20Pratap%20Singh%20said%20he%20had%20complained%20to%20the%20party%20supremo%20against%20Maurya%2C%20following%20which%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20told%20his%20legislators%20to%20refrain%20from%20commenting%20on%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20another%20powerful%20SP%20MLA%20Manoj%20Pandey%2C%20who%20had%20organised%20a%20programme%20for%20Yadav%20to%20unveil%20a%20statue%20of%20Hindu%20deity%20Parshuram%2C%20an%20avatar%20of%20Vishnu%2C%20came%20out%20with%20the%20strongest%20censure%20of%20Maurya.%20Pandey%20called%20Maurya%20%E2%80%9Cdemented%E2%80%9D%20for%20not%20listening%20to%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20party%20supremo.%20%E2%80%9CA%20person%20who%20has%20lost%20his%20mental%20stability%2C%20will%20keep%20talking%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Pandey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaurya%20was%20upset%20by%20this%20long%20trajectory%20of%20criticism%20from%20his%20own%20colleagues.%20In%20his%20resignation%20letter%2C%20he%20explained%20his%20strategy%20of%20raking%20up%20the%20%E2%80%9Chonour%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Crespect%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20OBCs%2C%20SCs%20and%20Dalits%20to%20lure%20them%20back%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Cspider%20web%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20BJP.%20He%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20use%20%E2%80%9Cscientific%20temper%E2%80%9D%20to%20connect%20with%20these%20communities%20and%20increase%20the%20mass%20support%20of%20the%20SP.%20However%2C%20Maurya%20said%2C%20some%20%E2%80%9Csmall%20and%20big%20leaders%20tried%20to%20blunt%20this%20narrative%20by%20dismissing%20it%20as%20%E2%80%98Maurya%E2%80%99s%20personal%20statements%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20put%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20criminal%20proceedings%20against%20Maurya%20for%20his%20comments%20against%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamcharitmanas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20why%20it%20was%20being%20so%20%E2%80%9Ctouchy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20this%20means%20for%20the%20SP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20SP%20should%20have%20been%20preparing%20itself%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20sealing%20its%20alliances%2C%20it%20faces%20the%20task%20of%20firefighting%20a%20potentially%20damaging%20internal%20rebellion%20by%20important%20OBC%20leaders.%20Post%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20it%20has%20already%20lost%20two%20important%20allies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20in%20east%20UP%20and%20the%20RLD%20of%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20in%20west%20UP.%20The%20exit%20of%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20(Kameravadi)%20and%20Maurya%20will%20be%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20disaster%20for%20the%20SP%2C%20immediately%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaurya%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20not%20only%20coincides%20with%20the%20nomination%20for%20the%20RS%20polls%20but%20also%20closely%20follows%20the%20SP%20declaring%20Dharmendra%20Yadav%20as%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidate%20in%20Budaun.%20Maurya%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20Sanghmitra%20Maurya%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Budaun.%20She%20won%20in%202019%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket%20when%20her%20father%20was%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20BJP%20government.%20She%20had%20defeated%20Dharmendra%20Yadav%2C%20a%20cousin%20of%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20a%20former%20MP%20from%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Budaun%20seat%20and%20the%20RS%20berth%20out%20of%20bounds%2C%20there%20was%20a%20looming%20question%20on%20Sanghamitra%20Maurya%E2%80%99s%20political%20future.%20While%20her%20father%20shifted%20ranks%20to%20the%20SP%20in%202022%2C%20resigning%20as%20minister%2C%20she%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20BJP%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20will%20get%20complicated%20if%20Maurya%20decides%20to%20stay%20back%20in%20the%20SP%20and%20his%20daughter%20is%20fielded%20again%20by%20the%20BJP%20against%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20control%20damage%2C%20senior%20SP%20leader%20Ram%20Govind%20Chaudhary%20wrote%20to%20party%20president%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20requesting%20him%20to%20not%20accept%20Maurya%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20as%20it%20was%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20party%20to%20retain%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707989431000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15103522%2FUP.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fafter-rld-exit-now-sp-faces-a-new-crisis-in-up-over-commitment-towards-obcs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maurya's%20resignation%20not%20only%20coincides%20with%20the%20nomination%20for%20the%20RS%20polls%20but%20also%20closely%20follows%20the%20SP%20declaring%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidate%20in%20Budaun%20%E2%80%93%20where%20his%20daughter%20is%20currently%20the%20sitting%20BJP%20MP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fafter-rld-exit-now-sp-faces-a-new-crisis-in-up-over-commitment-towards-obcs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmers%20Protest%3A%20Barricades%2C%20Concertina%20Wire%2C%20and%20Spikes%20on%20the%20Road.%20So%2C%20What%E2%80%99s%20New%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15135546%2Fv2-Screenshot-2024-02-15-at-1.53.12-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20two%20days%20and%20two%20nights%20now%2C%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20trying%20to%20make%20their%20way%20to%20Delhi%20from%20Punjab%20have%20been%20attacked%20relentlessly%20with%20tear%20gas%20shells%20and%20rubber%20bullets%20at%20Shambhu%20Barrier%2C%20one%20of%20the%20borders%20that%20demarcates%20Punjab%20from%20Haryana.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20over%20100%20farmers%20have%20been%20injured.%20Journalists%20covering%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20spared%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20visuals%20emerging%20from%20Shambhu%20are%20difficult%20to%20watch%20%E2%80%93%20bloody%20heads%2C%20rubber%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ebullet%20wounds%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20desperate%20attempts%20to%20get%20tear%20gas%20out%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20eyes.%20For%20those%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20for%20any%20length%20of%20time%20or%20in%20any%20shape%20or%20form%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20borders%20in%202020-21%2C%20these%20scenes%20are%20even%20more%20difficult%20to%20watch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%2C%20after%20all%2C%20the%20same%20farmers%20one%20visited%20several%20times%20at%20Tikri%20and%20Singhu%20and%20shared%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elangar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with.%20These%20are%20also%20the%20same%20people%20who%20showed%20incredible%20fortitude%20and%20courage%20as%20they%20braved%20heat%2C%20cold%2C%20rain%20and%20non-stop%20calumny%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egodi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20media.%20These%20are%2C%20indeed%2C%20the%20same%20simple%20and%20unassuming%20folk%20who%20showed%20the%20world%20yet%20again%20that%20Gandhian%20non-violent%20resistance%20is%20still%20possible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20news%20coming%20in%20from%20the%20Haryana-Punjab%20border%20is%20sporadic%2C%20as%20X%20and%20Facebook%20accounts%20of%20farmer%20leaders%20and%20journalists%20in%20the%20area%20have%20been%20shut%20down.%20One%20has%20to%20look%20through%20a%20lot%20of%20YouTube%20videos%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20is%20happening%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I%20watched%20videos%20of%20various%20journalists%20covering%20the%20situation%20at%20Shambhu%2C%20I%20spotted%20a%20farmer%20that%20I%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLDyaogIbL1I%3Fsi%3DqJIlrBOqCTPNbYKU%5C%22%3Einterviewed%20at%20Tikri%20border%20in%20early%202021%20right%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20January%2026%20tractor%20rally%20that%20year.%20A%20giant%20of%20a%20man%2C%20he%20was%20difficult%20to%20forget.%20I%20remember%20his%20words%20had%20made%20an%20impression%20on%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLDyaogIbL1I%3Fsi%3DqJIlrBOqCTPNbYKU%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20roads%20that%20the%20government%20has%20dug%20up%2C%20barricaded%2C%20hammered%20huge%20spikes%20into%20them%2C%20whose%20money%20were%20those%20roads%20built%20with%3F%20Our%20tax%20money.%20This%20is%20wrong.%20We%20are%20feeling%20very%20bad.%20They%20are%20calling%20us%20Khalistanis%20and%20terrorists.%20When%20we%20stand%20at%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20borders%20and%20defend%20them%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20look%20like%20Khalistanis%20then%2C%20do%20we%3F%20First%20you%20use%20us%2C%20and%20then%20you%20call%20us%20Khalistanis.%20The%20tri-colour%20is%20precious%20to%20us%20because%20we%20have%20sacrificed%20so%20much%20to%20attain%20it!%20For%20them%20it%20may%20just%20be%20a%20piece%20of%20cloth%2C%20but%20for%20us%2C%20the%20tri-colour%20is%20our%20life!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-modi-government-used-british-era-law-to-give-itself-powers-to-suspend-internet%5C%22%3EFarmers%E2%80%99%20Protest%3A%20Modi%20Government%20Used%20British-Era%20Law%20to%20Give%20Itself%20Powers%20to%20Suspend%20Internet%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20voice%20rose%20as%20he%20went%20on%20to%20talk%20about%20Modi%20and%20the%20state%20of%20democracy%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CDemocracy%20is%20in%20very%20bad%20shape%20in%20our%20country.%20They%20say%20India%20is%20the%20biggest%20democracy%20in%20the%20world.%20But%20is%20it%3F%20Modiji%2C%20you%20made%20so%20many%20promises%20before%20coming%20to%20power.%20You%20told%20us%20you%20are%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echowkidaar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20we%20believed%20you%20and%20voted%20for%20you.%20But%20you%20haven%E2%80%99t%20fulfilled%20any%20of%20those%20promises.%20Has%20our%20income%20doubled%20as%20you%20promised%3F%20You%20said%20you%20would%20stand%20with%20the%20farmers%20through%20thick%20and%20thin%2C%20but%20every%20year%20you%20are%20decreasing%20our%20subsidy.%20Please%20read%20the%20Swaminathan%20commission%20report%20and%20give%20us%20our%20due!%20One%20last%20thing%2C%20did%20you%20see%20how%20they%20attacked%20us%20with%20tear%20gas%20as%20our%20convoy%20of%20tractors%20rolled%20into%20Delhi%20on%20November%2026%3F%20How%20can%20you%20treat%20people%20so%20inhumanely%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20that%20farmer%2C%20whose%20name%20unfortunately%20I%20did%20not%20record%2C%20literally%20nothing%20has%20changed.%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20has%20not%20become%20a%20legal%20guarantee%2C%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20loans%20have%20not%20been%20forgiven%2C%20and%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20killings%20continue%20to%20go%20scot-free.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20practically%20impossible%20to%20tell%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20photos%20of%20the%20concrete%20barriers%20and%20concertina%20wire%20in%202020%20and%202024.%20All%20that%20has%20changed%20is%20that%20the%20government%20is%20now%20firing%20at%20the%20farmers%20with%20rubber%20bullets%20and%20using%20drones%20to%20attack%20them%20with%20tear%20gas%2C%20a%20cruel%20and%20sick%20joke%2C%20given%20the%20promises%20made%20in%20this%20poster%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133504%2FGGNhRZsbcAAdMzd.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133504%2FGGNhRZsbcAAdMzd.png%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133504%2FGGNhRZsbcAAdMzd-300x300.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133504%2FGGNhRZsbcAAdMzd-150x150.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697278%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPoster%20about%20the%20Kisan%20Drone%20scheme.%20Photo%3A%20Author%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20I%20have%20called%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20farmers%20I%20met%20during%20the%202020-21%20protests.%20The%20odds%20are%20stacked%20against%20them%2C%20but%20their%20voices%20reveal%20no%20trace%20of%20fear%20or%20anxiety.%20Perha