2F2024%2F02%2F15135644%2FProton-Mail-logo.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20IT%20ministry%20decided%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%2014)%20to%20block%20the%20Proton%20Mail%20email%20service%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fit-ministry-looks-to-block-proton-mail-on-request-of-tamil-nadu-police-101707938167006.html%5C%22%3Ethe%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20ministry%20has%20not%20yet%20issued%20a%20final%20blocking%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20learnt%20that%20the%20ministry%20decided%20to%20block%20Proton%20Mail%20after%20a%20request%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20police%2C%20which%20said%20it%20was%20unable%20to%20trace%20the%20perpetrators%20behind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fchennai%2Fchennai-citys-popular-schools-receive-bomb-threat-mail-police-after-checking-declare-it-a-hoax%2Farticle67826026.ece%5C%22%3Ea%20hoax%20bomb%20threat%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20sent%20to%2013%20schools%20in%20the%20Chennai%20area%20last%20week%20using%20the%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20nodal%20officer%20representing%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20police%20said%20yesterday%20that%20attempts%20to%20trace%20the%20perpetrators%E2%80%99%20IP%20addresses%20and%20to%20seek%20help%20from%20the%20Interpol%20did%20not%20bear%20fruit%2C%20the%20newspaper%20also%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20officer%20was%20present%20at%20a%20committee%20meeting%20held%20as%20part%20of%20the%20online%20content%20blocking%20process%20relating%20to%20Section%2069A%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20of%20the%20IT%20ministry%20noted%20during%20the%20meeting%20that%20receiving%20information%20from%20Proton%20Mail%20on%20criminal%20matters%20was%20a%20recurrent%20problem%2C%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProton%2C%20the%20Swiss%20software%20company%20that%20offers%20the%20Proton%20Mail%20service%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20IT%20ministry%20had%20notified%20it%20about%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpotential%20block%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20it%20was%20considering%20a%20way%20to%20work%20with%20Indian%20authorities%20in%20order%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSKBN1ZS1L1%2F%5C%22%3ERussia%E2%80%99s%20government%20also%20decided%20to%20block%20Proton%20Mail%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020%2C%20saying%20Proton%20did%20not%20provide%20it%20with%20information%20on%20users%20who%20allegedly%20sent%20fake%20bomb%20threats%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20condemn%20this%20block%20as%20a%20misguided%20measure%20which%20only%20serves%20to%20harm%20ordinary%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20Proton%20had%20said%20then%20in%20a%20statement.%20It%20also%20said%20this%20to%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20the%20Indian%20IT%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20reported%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBlocking%20access%20to%20Proton%20is%20an%20ineffective%20and%20inappropriate%20response%20to%20the%20reported%20threats.%20It%20will%20not%20prevent%20cybercriminals%20from%20sending%20threats%20with%20another%20email%20service%20and%20will%20not%20be%20effective%20if%20the%20perpetrators%20are%20located%20outside%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Proton%20also%20told%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmails%20sent%20through%20Proton%20Mail%20are%20end-to-end%20encrypted%2C%20which%20means%20that%20no%20one%20except%20those%20communicating%20with%20each%20other%20using%20the%20service%20can%20read%20the%20messages%20they%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20service%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSKBN1ZS1L1%2F%5C%22%3Epopular%20among%20some%20journalists%20and%20activists%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%20focus%20on%20privacy%20and%20encryption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20its%20website%2C%20Proton%20says%20the%20data%20of%20its%20email%20service%20users%20are%20%E2%80%9Cprotected%20by%20strict%20Swiss%20privacy%20laws%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Swiss%20law%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fproton.me%2Flegal%2Flaw-enforcement%5C%22%3EProton%20is%20also%20required%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccooperate%20with%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20on%20criminal%20investigations%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20Swiss%20laws%20and%20privacy%20regulations%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20can%20include%20transmitting%20data%20via%20Swiss%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProton%20also%20offers%20virtual%20private%20network%20%E2%80%93%20popularly%20known%20as%20VPN%20%E2%80%93%20as%20well%20as%20password%20manager%20and%20cloud%20storage%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IT%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20reported%20decision%20comes%20just%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20Union%20government%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Caravan%3C%2Fem%3E%20magazine%20under%20Section%2069A%20of%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Funion-govt-uses-it-act-to-attack-press-freedom-asks-caravan-to-take-down-report%5C%22%3Easking%20it%20to%20take%20down%20an%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%20covering%20allegations%20of%20torture%20and%20murder%20against%20the%20Indian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20magazine%20was%20told%20that%20if%20it%20fails%20to%20take%20down%20the%20article%20from%20its%20website%20within%2024%20hours%2C%20the%20entire%20website%20would%20be%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegal%20news%20website%C2%A0%3Cem%3EArticle14%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20recent%20report%20cited%20experts%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Ftakedown-of-hate-tracker-highlights-secrecy-around-modi-govt-s-internet-censorship-practices-65c59c3549d5a%5C%22%3Edodged%20procedural%20safeguards%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20passing%20orders%20to%20block%20online%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BThese%20procedural%20safeguards%20are%20enough%20if%20followed%20diligently%20%E2%80%A6%20But%20you%20will%20see%20in%20practice%20that%20they%20are%20indiscriminately%20abandoned%2C%E2%80%9D%20Radhika%20Roy%2C%20counsel%20at%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EArticle14%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707986987000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15135644%2FProton-Mail-logo.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fit-ministry-decides-to-block-proton-mail-after-fake-bomb-threats-in-tamil-nadu-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20officer%20representing%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20police%20said%20during%20a%20content%20blocking%20committee%20meeting%20that%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20trace%20the%20perpetrators%20behind%20fake%20bomb%20threats%20sent%20to%20schools%20using%20Proton%20Mail.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fit-ministry-decides-to-block-proton-mail-after-fake-bomb-threats-in-tamil-nadu-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmers'%20Protest%3A%20Modi%20Government%20Used%20British-Era%20Law%20to%20Give%20Itself%20Powers%20to%20Suspend%20Internet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133759%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-15-at-1.36.06-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20legislation%20invoked%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20give%20itself%20powers%20to%20block%20internet%20services%20in%20Punjab%20last%20week%20as%20farmers%20prepared%20to%20launch%20their%20protest%2C%20is%20a%20British-era%20law%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcentre-used-british-era-act-to-block-internet-in-punjab-ahead-of-the-farmers-march%2Farticle67846087.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20context%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20emergency%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20safety%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20invoked%20its%20powers%20under%20the%20Temporary%20Suspension%20of%20Telecom%20Services%20(Public%20Emergency%20or%20Public%20Safety)%20Rules%2C%202017%20of%20the%20Indian%20Telegraph%20Act%2C%201885%2C%20to%20suspend%20internet%20within%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%2020%20police%20stations%20in%20Patiala%2C%20SAS%20Nagar%2C%20Bathinda%2C%20Sri%20Mukhtsar%20Sahib%2C%20Mansa%2C%20Sangrur%20and%20Fatehgarh%20Sahib%20since%20last%20week%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20a%20Punjab%20government%20official%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20the%20power%20to%20issue%20such%20orders%20under%20the%20Rules%20and%20that%20the%20Punjab%20government%20had%20not%20objected%20it.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP-ruled%20Haryana%20government%20issued%20orders%20to%20suspend%20internet%20services%20in%20that%20particular%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fpolicy%2Freport-summaries%2Fsuspension-of-telecom-services-internet-and-its-impact%5C%22%3Ereport%20%3C%2Fa%3Esubmitted%20on%20December%202021%2C%20the%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%20on%20communications%20and%20information%20technology%20had%20observed%20that%20internet%20shutdowns%20have%20implications%20on%20national%20economy%2C%20freedom%20of%20press%2C%20education%20and%20healthcare%20services.%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%202017%20Rules%2C%20telecom%2Finternet%20shutdowns%20may%20be%20ordered%20on%20grounds%20of%20public%20emergency%20and%20public%20safety.%20Public%20emergency%20and%20public%20safety%20have%20not%20been%20defined%20in%20the%201885%20Act%20or%20the%202017%20Rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Shashi%20Tharoor-led%20parliamentary%20committee%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20dozen%20accounts%20on%20X%20(formerly%20called%20Twitter)%20and%20Facebook%20which%20functioned%20as%20official%20pages%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20organisations%20and%20unions%20ahead%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%20have%20been%20withheld%20in%20India%20seemingly%20upon%20government%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-social-media-accounts-withheld-protest%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Agenda%20Is%20to%20Silence%20Us%E2%80%99%3A%20Key%20Social%20Media%20Accounts%20Withheld%2C%20Farmers%20Vow%20to%20Boycott%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20Meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EX%20accounts%20and%20Facebook%20pages%20of%20prominent%20farmer%20leaders%20like%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20the%20coordinator%20of%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%2C%20Tejveer%20Singh%20Ambala%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20BKU%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Ramandeep%20Singh%20Mann%2C%20Surjit%20Singh%20Phull%20from%20BKU%20Krantikari%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Harpal%20Sangha%2C%20Ashok%20Danoda%20from%20Haryana%20and%20many%20others%20have%20been%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20official%20pages%20which%20supported%20the%20movement%20and%20posted%20updates%20on%20it%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%C2%A0%20%40Tractor2twitr_P%20run%20by%20Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%20and%20Progressive%20Farmers%20Front%2C%20run%20by%20Guramneet%20Singh%20Mangat%20%E2%80%93%20are%20also%20banned%20by%20the%20government.%20BKU%20(SBS)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20farmer%20unions%20which%20was%20leading%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20from%20Ambala%2C%20Haryana.%20%E2%80%98Gaon%20Sawera%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20page%20run%20by%20independent%20journalist%20Mandeep%20Punia%20and%20his%20personal%20page%20has%20been%20withheld.%20Punia%20was%20arrested%20during%20the%202021%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707984664000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133759%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-15-at-1.36.06-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-modi-government-used-british-era-law-to-give-itself-powers-to-suspend-internet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20time%20the%20Union%20government%20suspended%20internet%20within%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%2020%20police%20stations%20in%20Patiala%2C%20SAS%20Nagar%2C%20Bathinda%2C%20Sri%20Mukhtsar%20Sahib%2C%20Mansa%2C%20Sangrur%20and%20Fatehgarh%20Sahib.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-modi-government-used-british-era-law-to-give-itself-powers-to-suspend-internet%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20is%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene%20-%20and%20why%20did%20she%20tell%20David%20Cameron%20to%20'kiss%20my%20a**'%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707984660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-marjorie-taylor-greene_6456338.jpg%3F20240215104710%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwho-is-marjorie-taylor-greene-and-why-did-she-tell-david-cameron-to-kiss-my-a-13072025%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Republican%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene%20has%20told%20David%20Cameron%20to%20%26quot%3Bkiss%20my%20ass%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwho-is-marjorie-taylor-greene-and-why-did-she-tell-david-cameron-to-kiss-my-a-13072025%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwho-is-marjorie-taylor-greene-and-why-did-she-tell-david-cameron-to-kiss-my-a-13072025%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwho-is-marjorie-taylor-greene-and-why-did-she-tell-david-cameron-to-kiss-my-a-13072025%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20One%20Initiative%20is%20Taking%20Paediatric%20Cancer%20Care%20To%20The%20Doorsteps%20of%202500%20Kids%20in%20Rural%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildhood%20cancers%20are%20a%20rising%20problem%20globally.%20The%20WHO%20states%20that%20over%20four%20lakh%20children%20develop%20cancer%20each%20year%2C%20with%20India%20accounting%20for%2050%2C000%20of%20these%20cases.%20While%20survival%20rates%20are%20high%20in%20high-income%20countries%2C%20India%20still%20faces%20the%20problems%20of%20lack%20of%20diagnosis%2C%20delayed%20diagnosis%2C%20access%20to%20care%2C%20and%20continuation%20of%20treatment.%20An%20ICMR%20(Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research)%20paper%20states%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20specific%20policy%20work%20to%20bring%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333669%2Fbasic-health-tests-we-should-do-regularly-heart-lungs-kidneys-cancer-detection-inspiring-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20childhood%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20control%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20an%20ICMR-NCDIR%20(National%20Centre%20for%20Disease%20Informatics%20and%20Research)%20study%20found%20that%20a%20dedicated%20paediatric%20oncology%20department%20was%20available%20in%2041.6%25%20of%20government%20hospitals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20instance%2C%2010-year-old%20Saksham%20(name%20changed).%20Residing%20in%20Timbi%20village%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20playful%20child%20started%20experiencing%20unexplained%20fatigue%2C%20frequent%20infections%2C%20and%20fever%20in%202022.%20His%20father%2C%20Ramesh%20(name%20changed)%2C%20a%20farmer%2C%20consulted%20local%20doctors%20(for%20which%20he%20had%20to%20travel%2020%20km)%2C%20but%20none%20of%20the%20medications%20they%20gave%20worked%20on%20the%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaksham%20was%20then%20taken%20almost%2090%20km%20away%2C%20to%20%E2%80%98The%20Himalayan%20Hospital%E2%80%99%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20where%20blood%20tests%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20Acute%20Lymphoblastic%20Leukaemia%20(ALL)%2C%20a%20type%20of%20blood%20cancer.%20Father%20to%20six%20children%2C%20with%20barely%20any%20income%2C%20Ramesh%20had%20already%20spent%20about%20Rs%2050%2C000%20for%20his%20travels%20and%20different%20treatments.%20The%20treatment%20for%20ALL%2C%20doctors%20estimated%2C%20would%20be%20about%20Rs%208%20lakhs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20lost%20all%20hope.%20My%20income%20was%20just%20enough%20to%20feed%20my%20family.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20do%20and%20how%20to%20save%20my%20child%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctor%20then%20informed%20Ramesh%20about%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Hans%20Bal%20Aarogya%20Karyakram%2C%20which%20supports%20cancer%20treatment%20and%20bone%20marrow%20transplants.%20Working%20with%20the%20hospital%20and%20the%20family%2C%20the%20programme%20has%20covered%20the%20cost%20of%20chemotherapy%2C%20bone%20marrow%20transplant%2C%20blood%20transfusions%20and%20other%20medical%20expenses%20for%20Saksham%2C%20who%20is%20now%20on%20the%20road%20to%20recovery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hans%20Bal%20Aarogya%20Karyakram%2C%20run%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%2C%20is%20bridging%20the%20gap%20of%20financial%20access%20for%20children%20who%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20treatment%20for%20critical%20diseases%20like%20cancer.%20So%20far%2C%20over%202%2C500%20children%20have%20benefited%20from%20this%20initiative%20and%20have%20received%20life-saving%20treatments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20parents%20access%20quality%20cancer%20care%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20853px)%20100vw%2C%20853px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHans1-1707980361.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hans%20Bal%20Aarogya%20Karyakram%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%2C%20is%20closing%20the%20financial%20gap%20for%20children%20unable%20to%20afford%20treatment%20for%20serious%20illnesses%20such%20as%20cancer.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHans1-1707980361.jpg%20853w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHans1-1707980361-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHans1-1707980361-500x750.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHans1-1707980361-768x1152.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHans1-1707980361-150x225.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341893%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Bal%20Aarogya%20Karyakram%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Government%2C%20is%20closing%20the%20financial%20gap%20for%20children%20unable%20to%20afford%20treatment%20for%20serious%20illnesses%2C%20such%20as%20cancer.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEstablished%20in%202017%20in%20close%20partnership%20with%20the%20state%20government%2C%20the%20programme%20provides%20free%20treatment%20to%20children%20aged%200-18%20years%20who%20are%20suffering%20from%20critical%20diseases%20or%20conditions%2C%20complementing%20the%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Swasthya%20Karyakram%20(RBSK)%20and%20subsequently%2C%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20schemes%20by%20supporting%20treatment%20for%20conditions%20outside%20the%20schemes%E2%80%99%20purview%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20District%20Early%20Intervention%20Centers%20(DEICs)%2C%20established%20under%20the%20RBSK%2C%20identify%20infants%20and%20children%20with%20developmental%20delays%2C%20disabilities%20and%20diseases.%20Once%20identified%2C%20these%20children%20are%20referred%20to%20two%20empanelled%20medical%20colleges%2C%20namely%20The%20Himalayan%20Hospital%20(Swami%20Ram%20Himalayan%20University)%20and%20Shri%20Mahant%20Indresh%20Hospital.%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20has%20partnered%20with%20these%20two%20colleges%20and%20reimburses%20the%20treatment%20expenses%20for%20diseases%20like%20cancer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20programme%20is%20broadly%20designed%2C%2090%20percent%20of%20the%20patients%20who%20need%20support%20are%20cancer%20patients%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322528%2Futtar-pradesh-cancer-survivor-sandeep-kumar-runs-digiswasthya-free-medical-teleconsultation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecancer%20treatments%3C%2Fa%3E%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20and%20money.%20The%20average%20cost%20of%20treating%20common%20cancers%20in%20children%20like%20ALL%20and%20Acute%20Myeloid%20Leukaemia%20(AML)%20can%20easily%20range%20from%20Rs%205-15%20lakhs%20or%20even%20more%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20complexity%20of%20the%20disease%20at%20the%20time%20of%20diagnosis.%20Most%20of%20the%20children%20who%20come%20in%20for%20treatment%20are%20either%20infants%2C%20or%20between%20the%20age%20group%20of%205-8.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommon%20cancers%20in%20children%20are%20different%20from%20those%20seen%20in%20adults.%20Dr%20BP%20Kalra%2C%20Professor%20of%20Pediatrics%2C%20Department%20of%20Pediatrics%2C%20Himalayan%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%2C%20Dehradun%20states%20that%20leukaemias%20(cancer%20of%20blood-forming%20tissues)%2C%20lymphomas%20(cancer%20of%20the%20lymphatic%20system)%20are%20the%20most%20common%2C%20followed%20by%20brain%20and%20bone%20cancer%20and%20tumours%20like%20the%20Wilms%20Tumour%20(renal%20cancer).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20see%20that%20most%20commonly%2C%20children%20get%20cancer%20in%20the%20first%20or%20second%20year%20of%20life%2C%20or%20in%20the%205-10%20age%20group.%20In%20the%20school-going%20age%20group%2C%20leukaemias%20and%20lymphomas%20are%20most%20common.%20The%20outcome%20is%20generally%20good%20in%20this%20age%20group%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Kalra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Himalayan%20Institute%20caters%20to%20children%20from%20across%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20sometimes%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20more.%C2%A0%20The%20reason%2C%20the%20doctor%20adds%2C%20is%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20facilities%20for%20treatment%2C%20which%20makes%20parents%20and%20children%20travel%20far%20and%20wide%20for%20basic%20access.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20needed%20for%20good%20outcomes%2C%20according%20to%20Dr%20Kalra%2C%20is%20an%20early%2C%20prompt%2C%20correct%20diagnosis%20which%20should%20be%20followed%20by%20effective%2C%20evidence-based%20therapy%20after%20which%20supportive%20care%20is%20paramount.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%202%2C500%20children%20get%20cancer%20treatment%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHans2-1707980359.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Camps%20by%20the%20the%20District%20Early%20Intervention%20Centers%20(DEICs)%20identify%20infants%20and%20children%20with%20developmental%20delays%2C%20disabilities%20and%20diseases.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHans2-1707980359.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHans2-1707980359-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHans2-1707980359-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHans2-1707980359-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHans2-1707980359-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341892%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECamps%20by%20the%20District%20Early%20Intervention%20Centers%20(DEICs)%20identify%20infants%20and%20children%20with%20developmental%20delays%2C%20disabilities%20and%20diseases.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildhood%20cancer%20management%20in%20Low%20and%20Middle-Income%20Countries%20(LMICs)%2C%20including%20India%2C%20is%20characterised%20by%20delayed%20diagnosis%20and%20treatment%20initiation%2C%20inadequate%2Fincomplete%20treatment%20and%20low%20survival%20rate%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20Indian%20Cancer%20Society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20starters%2C%20parents%20must%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20common%20symptoms%20and%20go%20to%20a%20doctor%20when%20they%20notice%20these%20including%3A%20recurrent%20fevers%2C%20loss%20of%20appetite%2C%20loss%20of%20weight%2C%20swelling%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20body%2C%20persistent%20pain%2C%20sudden%20tiredness%2C%20fatigue%2C%20headaches%2C%20any%20lumps%20or%20mass.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20first%20step%20where%20families%20notice%20symptoms%20and%20access%20care%2C%20the%20second%20step%20is%20clinical%20evaluation%20and%20diagnosis.%20Facilities%20like%20the%20DEIC%20should%20be%20able%20to%20help%20in%20this%20step.%20The%20last%20and%20most%20crucial%20step%20is%20accessibility%20to%20treatment.%20As%20the%20majority%20of%20public%20hospitals%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303740%2Fresearcher-quits-job-to-build-non-invasve-device-to-detect-breast-cancer-thermalytix-niramai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaediatric%20oncology%20care%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20parents%20either%20have%20to%20take%20them%20far%20to%20a%20government%20hospital%20that%20has%20the%20treatment%2C%20or%20go%20to%20a%20private%20hospital%20nearby.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20trusts%20like%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20is%20very%20important%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20as%20they%20help%20families%20afford%20quality%20healthcare%20and%20save%20the%20lives%20of%20their%20children%20through%20timely%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kalra%20says%20that%20his%20biggest%20request%20to%20parents%20is%20to%20continue%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CParents%20must%20remain%20hopeful%20and%20continue%20treatment.%20The%20results%20are%20good%20and%20most%20children%20do%20well%2C%20after%20early%20diagnosis.%20We%20are%20thankful%20to%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20which%20makes%20it%20possible%20for%20so%20many%20children%20to%20access%20treatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Kalra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hans%20Bal%20Arogya%20Karyakram%2C%20which%20has%20been%20working%20on%20ground%20since%202017%2C%20has%20helped%20over%202%2C518%20children.%20A%20medical%20audit%20found%20that%20the%20survival%20rates%20of%20children%20had%20improved%20by%20more%20than%2080%25%20post-intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20success%20of%20and%20the%20learnings%20from%20the%20programme%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20is%20now%20ready%20to%20expand%20its%20support%20to%20children%20suffering%20from%20cancer%20under%20its%20Hans%20Paediatric%20Care%20programme%20and%20extending%20services%20to%20RN%20Tagore%20Hospital%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20G%20Kuppuswamy%20Naidu%20Memorial%20Hospital%20in%20Coimbatore%2C%20Narayana%20Multispeciality%20Hospital%20in%20Howrah%20and%20SGVP%20Hospital%20in%20Ahmedabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20access%20to%20cancer%20treatment%20possible%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341755%2Fcongenital-heart-disease-in-babies-treatment-surgery-provided-by-hans-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20across%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20location.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20way%20out.%20The%20disease%20can%20happen%20to%20anyone.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20lose%20hope%20and%20have%20patience%20and%20faith%20in%20your%20doctor.%20Try%20the%20treatment%20and%20complete%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Kalra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%3A%20The%20Hans%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707982174000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHans1-1707980361.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341889%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Hans%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Bal%20Aarogya%20Karyakram%20supports%20paediatric%20oncology%20care%20for%20children%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20It%20has%20provided%20a%20total%20financial%20aid%20of%20Rs%208.5%20crore%20to%20children%20from%20underprivileged%20backgrounds%20who%20need%20this%20life-saving%20treatment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341889%2Fhans-foundation-bal-aarogya-karyakram-childhood-cancer-paediatric-oncology-leukaemia-lymphoma%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Striking%20Workers%20Battle%20Hotel%20Owned%20By%20Union%20Pension%20Fund%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20union%20for%20hotel%20workers%20says%20the%20carpenters'%20pension%20fund%20should%20be%20pressuring%20the%20Hyatt%20Regency%20LAX%20to%20reach%20a%20deal.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707954527000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F65cd1551230000310080881f.jpeg%3Fops%3D1