%20before%20Mahesh%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20from%20customers%20about%20this%20fruit%2C%20which%20heavily%20impacted%20the%20crop%E2%80%99s%20demand.%20%E2%80%9CNobody%20knew%20what%20dragon%20fruit%20was.%20After%20we%20managed%20to%20get%20some%20produce%2C%20we%20took%20it%20to%20the%20market.%20People%20doubted%20that%20this%20would%20even%20make%20any%20sale%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20overcome%20these%20challenges%2C%20Mahesh%20opened%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20to%20make%20farmers%20aware%20about%20the%20perks%20of%20dragon%20fruit%20farming%20which%20in%20turn%20led%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20consumption%20of%20the%20fruit.%20Over%20time%2C%20he%20gained%20good%20viewership%20and%20started%20attracting%20farmers%20to%20his%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20progressive%20farmer%20has%20become%20an%20example%20for%20several%20other%20farmers%20in%20the%20region.%20He%20has%20also%20opened%20the%20doors%20of%20his%20%E2%80%98Rukmini%20Farms%E2%80%99%20to%20serve%20as%20demonstration%20fields%20for%20others%20who%20wish%20to%20grow%20dragon%20fruits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20farm%20has%20been%20visited%20by%20at%20least%2035%2C000%20farmers%20from%20across%20Maharashtra.%20Of%20these%2C%20he%20has%20trained%20and%20helped%20500%20switch%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291638%2Fdoctor-does-organic-dragon-fruit-farming-helps-farmers-free-training-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edragon%20fruit%20cultivation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Mahesh%20has%20developed%20a%20good%20customer%20base%20in%20the%20nearby%20Sangli%20and%20Kolhapur%20markets%20where%20he%20manages%20to%20sell%20his%20seasonal%20produce%20of%20at%20least%20200%20tonnes%2C%20earning%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%202%20crores%20from%20his%2020-acre%20dragon%20fruit%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3